0However%2C%20the%20company%20didn't%20say%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20use%20the%20tech%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20beta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20complete%2C%20people%20can%20use%20Vitruvius%20to%20create%20floor%20plans%20and%20renderings%20%E2%80%94%20while%20considering%20requirements%20like%20budgets%20and%20permits%20%E2%80%94%20of%20their%20ideal%20printed%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHomeowners%20with%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20designing%20printed%20homes%20would%20be%20able%20to%20use%20Vitruvius%20instead%20of%20hiring%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprohibitively%20expensive%E2%80%9D%20architect%2C%20Yashar%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20rendering%20of%20a%203D%20printed%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0b17ece7f1785b2e8fc3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPictured%20is%20an%20example%20of%20Vitruvius's%20rendering.%3Cp%3EIcon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20future%2C%20I%20believe%20nearly%20all%20construction%20will%20be%20done%20by%20robots%2C%20and%20nearly%20all%20construction-related%20information%20will%20be%20processed%20and%20managed%20by%20AI%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Icon's%20CEO%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchitects%20could%20use%20Vitruvius%20to%20%26quot%3Baccelerate%26quot%3B%20the%20home%20design%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20these%20four%20new%20products%20%E2%80%94%20the%20printer%2C%20printing%20material%2C%20catalog%2C%20and%20AI%20system%20%E2%80%94%20Yashar%20said%20Icon%20could%20create%20higher-quality%20and%20more%20affordable%20dwellings%20without%20%E2%80%9Csacrificing%20dignity%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20beauty.%E2%80%9D%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rendering%20of%203d%20printed%20buildings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0b21b90413ab