pdf%5C%22%3Enew%20pilot%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20lower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-refinance-closing-costs%5C%22%3Erefinance%20closing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalled%20the%20%26quot%3Btitle%20acceptance%20pilot%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20program%20would%20waive%20the%20requirement%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fconforming-loans%5C%22%3Econforming%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy%20on%20certain%20refinance%20mortgages.%20This%20would%20lower%20eligible%20borrowers'%20closing%20costs%2C%20meaning%20they'd%20need%20less%20cash%20to%20close%20on%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20announced%20the%20pilot%20at%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%2C%20where%20he%20outlined%20several%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-lower-cost-homeownership-hopeful-homebuyers-2024-3%5C%22%3Ehousing%20proposals%20aimed%20at%20making%20homeownership%20more%20affordable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20the%20FHFA's%20new%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20works%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20FHFA's%20new%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FHFA%2C%20which%20oversees%20mortgage%20investors%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20will%20allow%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhen-to-refinance-mortgage%5C%22%3Emortgage%20refinances%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20sold%20to%20Fannie%20or%20Freddie%20without%20requiring%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20or%20refinance%20a%20home%2C%20a%20title%20search%20is%20completed%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20unknown%20parties%20have%20a%20claim%20to%20the%20property.%20Title%20insurance%20then%20protects%20the%20policyholder%20from%20losses%20related%20to%20a%20title%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20are%20required%20to%20purchase%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20significant%20out-of-pocket%20cost.%20The%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20waives%20this%20cost%20for%20eligible%20refinance%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20currently%20a%20temporary%20program%20that%20is%20small%20in%20scope.%20Only%20borrowers%20who%20have%20more%20than%2020%25%20equity%20in%20their%20home%20and%20live%20in%20%26quot%3Bselect%20geographies%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20eligible%2C%20says%20the%20FHFA.%20It%20will%20also%20only%20be%20available%20on%20loans%20that%20have%20been%20deemed%20to%20have%20low%20title%20risk%20based%20on%20an%20automated%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Potential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%5C%22%3EPotential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20eligible%20for%20this%20program%2C%20how%20much%20you%20could%20save%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20a%20title%20insurance%20policy%20typically%20costs%20in%20your%20area.%20The%20average%20homeowner%20could%20save%20%24750%20on%20their%20closing%20costs%20thanks%20to%20this%20new%20program%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Ffact-sheet-president-biden-announces-plan-to-lower-housing-costs-for-working-families%2F%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20FHFA%20says%20that%20savings%20could%20range%20between%20%24300%20to%20%241%2C500.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%5C%22%3EPushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20the%20mortgage%20and%20title%20insurance%20industries%20overall%20weren't%20pleased%20with%20this%20announcement.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alta.org%2Fnews-and-publications%2Fpress-release%2FALTA-Says-White-House-Attack-on-Title-Insurance-Offer