ie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrozen%20fries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20cooked%20a%20pound%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc8a64d9934781f2760a61f75359c87ec66540680c89407ff95d5e18bd90c4c09%26postID%3D65d50d5ebad86bdcf7719201%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fninja-foodi-dualzone-air-fryer-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.target.com%252Fp%252Fore-ida-gluten-free-frozen-extra-crispy-fast-food-fries-26oz%252F-%252FA-13257873%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOre-Ida%20Extra%20Crispy%20Fast%20Food%20French%20Fries%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20unit%20for%20eight%20minutes%20at%20400%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20shaking%20the%20basket%20halfway%20through.%20We%20checked%20for%20a%20golden%20brown%20color%20and%20added%20more%20time%20if%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ninja%20was%20slow.%20It%20took%2020%20minutes%20to%20finish%20the%20cooking%20process%2C%20more%20than%20twice%20as%20long%20as%20the%20top%20performers.%20However%2C%20the%20resulting%20fries%20were%20outstanding.%20They%20were%20evenly%20cooked%20and%20crispy%2C%20reminding%20me%20of%20the%20best%20fast-food%20fries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHand-cut%20fries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20every%20air%20fryer%20we%20test%2C%20we%20also%20cook%20homemade%20fries.%20We%20cut%20a%20pound%20of%20potatoes%20into%20fry-shaped%20pieces%2C%20soak%20them%20in%20cold%20water%20for%20about%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20dry%20them%2C%20and%20toss%20the%20fries%20with%20olive%20oil%20and%20salt.%20We%20air%20fry%20them%20at%20375%20degrees%20for%2015%20minutes%20and%20check%20for%20doneness.%20If%20they%20aren't%20crispy%2C%20we%20add%20more%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20air%20fryers%20struggle%20with%20this%20test%2C%20taking%20longer%20than%2015%20minutes%20or%20producing%20uneven%20results.%20While%20the%20Ninja%20Foodi%20DualZone%20XL%20wa