0Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slashfilm.com%2F1536025%2Fmoviepass-downfall-worse-than-you-realize%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlash%20Film%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%2C%20I%20got%20to%20witness%20South%20by%20Southwest's%20opening%20weekend%2C%20which%20was%20dominated%20by%20the%20streaming%20heavyweights%20Netflix%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Paramount%2B%2C%20with%20a%20cameo%20from%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20and%20Amazon%20kicked%20off%20the%20festival%20by%20promoting%20their%20upcoming%20sci-fi%20series.%20Netflix%20held%20a%20premiere%20for%20%26quot%3B3%20Body%20Problem%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Amazon%20built%20an%20interactive%20postapocalyptic%20world%20to%20promote%20%26quot%3BFallout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Date%20projected%20onto%20steel%20grid%20for%20Netflix's%20'3%20Body%20Problem'%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f074cbce7f1785b2e8d8fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix's%203D%20projection%20for%20%26quot%3B3%20Body%20Problem%26quot%3B%20stopped%20people%20in%20their%20tracks.%3Cp%3ENathan%20McAlone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ENetflix%20competed%20with%20Amazon%20for%20who%20could%20make%20the%20biggest%20sci-fi%20splash%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20way%20to%20Netflix's%20Friday%20evening%20premiere%20of%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3B3%20Body%20Problem%26quot%3B%20(streaming%20March%2021)%20%E2%80%94%20created%20by%20former%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20showrunners%20David%20Benioff%20and%20D.B.%20Weiss%2C%20along%20with%20Alexander%20Woo%20%E2%80%94%20I%20passed%20a%20menacing%203D%20projection%20promoting%20it%20that%20was%20stopping%20passersby%20in%20their%20tracks.%20When%20