review-game-of-thrones-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethough%2C%20as%20my%20colleague%20Palmer%20Haasch%3C%2Fa%3E%20rightly%20points%20out%20in%20her%20review%20of%20the%20series%2C%20the%201960s%20storyline%20is%20the%20most%20compelling%20part%2C%20and%20Zine%20Tseng's%20performance%20is%20a%20standout%20(the%20show%20has%20a%2075%25%20critics'%20score%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rottentomatoes.com%2Ftv%2F3_body_problem%2Fs01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERotten%20Tomatoes%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20evening%2C%20I%20spotted%20Bradley%20and%20some%20of%20his%20costars%20hobnobbing%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20with%20basketball%20star%20Blake%20Griffin%2C%20who%20has%20been%20gaining%20some%20traction%20in%20Hollywood%20with%20his%20company%20Mortal%20Media%20(Apple%20TV%2B's%20%26quot%3BHello%20Tomorrow!%2C%26quot%3B%20Hulu's%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Men%20Can't%20Jump%26quot%3B%20reboot).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dentist%20barber%20pulling%20teeth%20of%20man%20seated%20during%20Amazon%20interactive%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f07628ce7f1785b2e8d998%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20got%20my%20teeth%20%26quot%3Bpulled%26quot%3B%20by%20Amazon.%3Cp%3ENathan%20McAlone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20took%20a%20different%20tack%20from%20Netflix%20when%20promoting%20its%20%26quot%3BFallout%26quot%3B%20show%2C%20an%20adaption%20of%20the%20blockbuster%20video%20game%20series%20that%20will%20start%20streaming%20on%20April%2011.%20In%20a%20real-life%20recreation%20of%20the%20show's%20postapocalyptic%20world%2C%20you%20could%20barter%20with%20actors%20and%20lasso%20two-headed%20cows.%20I%20got%20my%20teeth%20%26quot%3Bpulled%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20barber-dentist%20and%20got%20a%20scorpion-filled%20lollipop%20in%20return.%20The%20crowd%20was%20having%20a%20ball%