e%20issue%20given%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20after%20a%20tug-of-war%20with%20Khattar%20over%20the%20control%20of%20CID%2C%20Mr%20Vij%20was%20stripped%20of%20charge%20of%20the%20department%2C%20and%20was%20later%20allocated%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%2C%20a%20six-time%20MLA%2C%20had%20then%20maintained%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20supreme%20and%20he%20could%20take%20away%20or%20divide%20any%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20back%2C%20when%20Khattar%20expanded%20his%20cabinet%2C%20Vij%20was%20divested%20of%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%20department%2C%20which%20was%20given%20to%20BJP's%20Hisar%20MLA%20Kamal%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202015%2C%20less%20than%20three%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Haryana%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20its%20own%2C%20Vij%20--%20who%20then%20held%20the%20health%20and%20sports%20departments%20--%20had%20taken%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20Khattar%20on%20X%2C%20posting%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20chief%20minister%20for%20taking%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20my%20departments.%20I'm%20relaxed.%26quot%3B%20Vij%20was%20then%20apparently%20upset%20with%20Khattar%20who%20had%20launched%20a%20number%20of%20programmes%20and%20schemes%20pertaining%20to%20departments%20handled%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%20was%20among%20the%20frontrunners%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20the%202014%20Haryana%20assembly%20polls.%20Mr%20Khattar%2C%20then%20a%20first-time%20MLA%2C%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20party's%20choice%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710268740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F