e%20asserted%20that%20Muslim%20citizens%20of%20India%20would%20not%20have%20their%20citizenship%20affected%20by%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D2013858%5C%22%3Eposted%20to%20the%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%206%3A43%20PM%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012).%20It%20is%20unclear%20why%20the%20release%20is%20now%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20contents%20were%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIB_India%2Fstatus%2F1767556925120544931%5C%22%3Eposted%20to%20the%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20X%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9CCAA%20myth%20busters%E2%80%9D%20but%20have%20since%20been%20deleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20aims%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%93%20and%20who%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%20and%20fears%20that%20it%20would%20disenfranchise%20many%20Muslims%20in%20India%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20sparked%20concerns%20and%20protests%20from%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliament%20passed%20the%20legislation%20in%20late%202019%20but%20the%20government%20notified%20its%20rules%20only%20yesterday.%20The%20CAA%20could%20not%20be%20implemented%20without%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20home%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20questions%20asked%20how%20the%20CAA%20would%20impact%20Islam%E2%80%99s%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20persecution%20of%20Minorities%20in%20those%20three%20Muslim%20countries%2C%20the%20name%20of%20Islam%20was%20badly%20tarnished%20all%20around%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20Islam%2C%20being%20a%20peaceful%20religion%2C%20never%20preaches%20or%20suggests%20hatred%2Fviolence%2Fany%20persecution%20on%20religious%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Act%20showing%20the%20compassion%20and%20compensation%20for%20the%20persecution%2C%20protects%20Islam%20from%20being%20tarnished%20in%20the%20name%20of%20persecution%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20said%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20not%20worry%20as%20CAA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20provision%20to%20impact%20their%20citizenship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20Muslims%20need%20not%20worry%20as%20CAA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20provision%20to%20impact%20their%20citizenship%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20present%2018%20crore%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20who%20have%20equal%20rights%20like%20their%20Hindu%20counterparts%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20Indian%20citizen%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20produce%20any%20document%20to%20prove%20his%20citizenship%20after%20this%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F712816436%2FPositive-narrative-on-Citizenship-Amendment-Act-2019%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Positive%20narrative%20on%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EPositive%20narrative%20on%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F712816436%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-jaOprIxJElHXGMV4hnUt%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7066666666666667%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Positive%20narrative%20on%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20India%20did%20not%20have%20a%20pact%20or%20agreement%20with%20either%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20or%20Bangladesh%20for%20repatriating%20illegal%20Muslim%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Citizenship%20Act%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20deal%20with%20the%20deportation%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20and%20therefore%20the%20concern%20of%20a%20section%20of%20the%20people%20including%20Muslims%20and%20students%20that%20CAA%20is%20against%20Muslim%20Minorities%20is%20unjustifiable%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20that%20asked%20why%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%20needed%20to%20be%20amended%2C%20the%20release%20cited%20a%20mix%20of%20providing%20amnesty%20to%20the%20minorities%20within%20the%20amendment%E2%80%99s%20ambit%20and%20%E2%80%98controlling%E2%80%99%20illegal%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20show%20the%20mercy%20on%20the%20persecuted%20minorities%20of%20those%20three%20countries%2C%20this%20Act%20gives%20opportunity%20to%20them%20as%20per%20the%20evergreen%20generous%20culture%20of%20India%20to%20get%20Indian%20Citizenship%20for%20their%20happy%20and%20prosperous%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20customise%20the%20Citizenship%20system%20and%20control%20the%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20there%20was%20need%20of%20this%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20introduction%20to%20the%20release%20also%20read%20that%20the%20CAA%20aimed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshow%20%E2%80%A6%20generous%20treatment%E2%80%9D%20to%20religious%20minorities%20who%20were%20persecuted%20in%20the%20three%20countries%20%E2%80%9Cas%20compensation%20for%20appeasing%20their%20persecution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710266108000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F19114548%2Fpib-hero-image.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpositive-narrative-on-caa-and-indian-muslims-released-by-home-ministry-goes-missing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Posted%20to%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau's%20website%20at%206%3A43%20PM%2C%20the%20release%20said%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%9Cprotects%20Islam%20from%20being%20tarnished%20in%20the%20name%20of%20persecution%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20unclear%20why%20it%20is%20now%20unavailable%20from%20its%20original%20webpage%20on%20the%20bureau's%20site.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpositive-narrative-on-caa-and-indian-muslims-released-by-home-ministry-goes-missing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emraan%20admits%20actors%20are%20suckers%20for%20attention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710266085000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108442703%2Cimgsize-23642.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Femraan-hashmi-admits-actors-are-suckers-for-attention-if-anyone-claims-theyre-not-in-the-industry-for-the-money-or-fame-theyre-lying%2Farticleshow%2F108442724.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108442724.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEmraan%20Hashmi%20recently%20talked%20about%20how%20his%20career%20has%20changed%20over%20time.%20He%20mentioned%20that%20when%20he%20first%20started%20out%2C%20he%20was%20mostly%20interested%20in%20the%20perks%2C%20money%2C%20and%20fame%20that%20came%20with%20his%20job.%20Even%20though%20he%20did%20have%20some%20passion%20for%20acting%2C%20it%20wasn't%20as%20strong%20as%20his%20desir