h%20died%20at%20about%2011%3A30%20GMT%20on%2011%20March%20and%20%26quot%3Bwill%20never%20be%20forgotten%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20video%20message%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20see%20everyone%20speaking%20about%20Leah%20and%20how%20amazing%20she%20is%20and%20how%20much%20she%20helped%20everyone.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20never%20let%20Leah%20be%20forgotten.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20boyfriend%20shared%20that%20Ms%20Smith%20read%20all%20the%20comments%20followers%20shared%20with%20her%20during%20her%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20said%20anything%20nice%20ever%2C%20it%20means%20more%20than%20you%20realise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20brother%20Liam%20also%20commented%20on%20the%20video%20to%20%26quot%3Bthank%20everyone%20for%20all%20they%20have%20done%20for%20Leah%20and%20this%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20TikTok%20follower%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLeah%20Smith%20you%20were%20amazing%20and%20so%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20best%20friend%20Vikki%20posted%20an%20update%20to%20thank%20everyone%20for%20their%20support%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20love%20could%20have%20saved%20her%20she%20would%20have%20lived%20forever%20and%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20before%20her%20diagnosis%2C%20Ms%20Smith%20spoke%20openly%20on%20TikTok%20about%20her%2010-month%20battle%20with%20back%20pain.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20sudden%20numbness%20in%20her%20left%20leg%20that%20became%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20leading%20her%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Ewing's%20Sarcoma%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEwing's%20sarcoma%20is%20an%20uncommon%20bone%20cancer%20primarily%20diagnosed%20in%20teenagers%20(aged%2010%20to%2020)%20according%20to%20the%20NHS%20%5BNational%20Health%20Service%5D.%20Symptoms%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20tumour's%20location%20and%20size%20but%20typically%20include%20worsening%20pain%2C