3347%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgoogles-ai-chatbot-gemini-no-longer-talks-about-elections-out-of-an-abundance-of-caution-13093347%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMaybe%20It's%20About%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%26quot%3B%3A%20ML%20Khattar%20On%20BJP's%20Haryana%20Revamp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20he%20resigned%20as%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20Tuesday%20hinted%20that%20he%20may%20be%20fielded%20by%20the%20party%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khattar%20also%20said%20he%20has%20come%20to%20know%20that%20the%20JJP%20has%20decided%20to%20contest%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20said%20the%20party%20leadership%20has%20told%20him%20that%20another%20responsibility%20will%20be%20given.%20%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20decided%20soon.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20it%20is%20about%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20possible...whatever%20the%20parliamentary%20board%20(of%20BJP)%20decides%2C%20I%20will%20abide%20by%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20speculations%20that%20Mr%20Khattar%20may%20be%20asked%20to%20contest%20from%20Karnal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20and%20all%2013%20other%20members%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20council%20of%20ministers%20submitted%20their%20resignations%20to%20the%20governor%20as%20a%20team%20of%20the%20party's%20central%20observers%20arrived%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20switch%20in%20Haryana%20came%20amid%20the%20ruling%20BJP-JJP%20coalition%20coming%20apart%2C%20though%20party%20leaders%20from%20both%20sides%20did%20not%20make%20immediate%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20replaced%20Mr%20Khattar%20with%20OBC%20leader%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20who%20was%20later%2