ala%2C%20Anoop%20Dhanak%20and%20Devender%20Singh%20Babli%20--%20were%20not%20reinducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Haryana%20president%20Saini%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20state's%20new%20chief%20minister%20hours%20after%20Khattar%20and%20his%20cabinet%20ministers%20resigned%20from%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20others%20took%20the%20oath%20as%20members%20of%20the%20new%20council%20of%20ministers%20along%20with%20Saini.%20They%20are%20BJP%20leaders%20Kanwar%20Pal%2C%20Mool%20Chand%20Sharma%2C%20Jai%20Parkash%20Dalal%20and%20Banwari%20Lal%20and%20independent%20MLA%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Chautala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20JJP's%20Haryana%20unit%20chief%20Nishan%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20meeting%20of%20the%20party%20was%20held%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20father%2C%20Dr%20Ajay%20Singh%20Chautala.%20All%20issues%20were%20discussed%20in%20the%20meeting.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20Ajay%20Chautala's%20birthday%20on%20Wednesday%20will%20be%20observed%20by%20holding%20Nav%20Sankalp%20rally%20in%20Hisar.%20Whatever%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20will%20be%20informed%20in%20the%20rally%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishan%20Singh%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20congratulated%20Mr%20Saini%20who%20took%20oath%20as%20new%20CM.%20Notably%2C%20with%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JJP%20remaining%20non-committal%20over%20jointly%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20earlier%20maintained%20that%20post-poll%20alliance%20with%20JJP%20was%20meant%20only%20for%20running%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20on%20breaking%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JJP%2C%20Karnal%20MP%20Sanjay%20Bhatia%20told%20reporters%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20that%20there%20is%20no%20official%20statement%20that%20the%20alliance%20with%20JJP%20has%20been%20broken.%20There%20is%20no%20statement%20either%20from%20the%20JJP%20or%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20said%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20a%20majority%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Independents%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20this%20alliance%20will%20remain%2C%20Mr%20Bhatia%20said%20the%20JJP%20had%20earlier%20given%20support.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20continue%20their%20support%2C%20who%20will%20have%20an%20objection%20to%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Asked%20whether%20doors%20are%20open%20for%20the%20JJP%2C%20Bhatia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20shut%20them%20(doors)%3F%20Nobody%20shut%20them.%26quot%3B%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20all%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20by%20large%20margins%20in%202019%2C%20appeared%20keen%20to%20fight%20the%20upcoming%20parliamentary%20polls%20on%20its%20own.%20It%20had%20forged%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP%20later%20after%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2041%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20assembly%20while%20the%20JJP%20has%2010.%20The%20ruling%20combine%20also%20enjoyed%20the%20support%20of%20six%20of%20the%20seven%20Independents%2C%20and%20is%20comfortably%20placed%20even%20without%20the%20JJP's%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20opposition%20Congress%20has%2030%20MLAs%20and%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20and%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%20(HLP)%20have%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710257940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9sohp6l_dushyant-chautala_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworked-day-and-night-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5225704%22%2C%22summary%22