he%20move%20as%20discriminatory%20and%20motivated%20by%20the%20approaching%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20It%20also%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20bar%20on%20Muslims%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20to%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuslims%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20can%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20Section%206%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20citizenship%20by%20naturalisation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20notified%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20to%20reduce%20the%20qualification%20period%20of%20application%20for%20citizenship%20from%2011%20to%205%20years%20for%20undocumented%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20headed%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20insisted%20that%20the%20Act%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20prevent%20any%20Muslim%2C%20who%20is%20persecuted%20in%20those%20Islamic%20countries%20(Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan)%20for%20practising%20their%20version%20of%20Islam%2C%20from%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20the%20existing%20laws%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCAA%20does%20not%20cancel%20the%20naturalisation%20laws.%20Therefore%2C%20any%20person%20including%20the%20Muslim%20migrants%20from%20any%20foreign%20country%2C%20seeking%20to%20be%20an%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20can%20apply%20for%20the%20same%20under%20the%20existing%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Muslims%20need%20not%20worry%20as%20CAA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20provision%20to%20impact%20their%20citizenship%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20present%2018%20crore%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20who%20have%20equal%20rights%20like%20their%20Hindu%20counterparts%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20seeking%20to%20allay%20fears%20of%20a%20section%20of%20Muslims%20regarding%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20erupted%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20against%20the%20decision%20to%20implement%20CAA%20as%20some%20fear%20the%20law%20could%20be%20used%20to%20declare%20them%20illegal%20immigrants%20and%20take%20away%20their%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20denies%20this%20and%20says%20the%20law%20is%20needed%20to%20help%20minorities%20facing%20persecution%20in%20Muslim-majority%20nations%20as%20per%20the%20%26quot%3Bevergreen%20generous%20culture%20of%20India%20to%20get%20Indian%20citizenship%20for%20their%20happy%20and%20prosperous%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Indian%20citizen%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20produce%20any%20document%20to%20prove%20citizenship%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%20doesn't%20deal%20with%20the%20deportation%20of%20illegal%20immigrants.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20concern%20of%20a%20section%20of%20the%20people%20including%20Muslims%20and%20students%20that%20CAA%20is%20against%20Muslim%20minorities%20is%20unjustifiable%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20due%20to%20the%20persecution%20of%20minorities%20in%20these%20three%20countries%2C%20Islam%20had%20been%20badly%20tarnished%20across%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20Islam%2C%20being%20a%20peaceful%20religion%2C%20never%20preaches%20or%20suggests%20hatred%2Fviolence%2Fany%20persecution%20on%20religious%20grounds.%20This%20Act%2C%20showing%20compassion%20and%20compensation%20for%20the%20persecution%2C%20protects%20Islam%20from%20being%20tarnished%20in%20the%20name%20of%20persecution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20need%20for%20the%20law%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%20to%20customise%20the%20citizenship%20system%20and%20control%20the%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20there%20was%20a%20need%20for%20this%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20of%20India%20grants%20the%20government%20the%20right%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20from%20a%20humanitarian%20perspective%20to%20refugees%20who%20faced%20religious%20persecution%20in%20their%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20has%20been%20implemented%20four%20years%20after%20the%20controversial%20law%20was%20passed.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20which%20committed%20to%20enacting%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%2C%20said%20the%20implementation%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710257460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fuj9njsbg_caa-rules_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-does-caa-put-any-restrictions-on-muslim-migrants-what-government-said-5226063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20today%20reiterated%20that%20the%20newly-implemented%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20or%20CAA%20doesn't%20curtail%20the%20freedom%20and%20opportunity%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20amid%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%20rank%20who%20term%20the%20move%20as%20discriminatory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-does-caa-put-any-restrictions-on-muslim-migrants-what-government-said-5226063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-does-caa-put-any-restrictions-on-muslim-migrants-what-government-said-5226063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-does-caa-put-any-restrictions-on-muslim-migrants-what-government-said-5226063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20aware%20of%20promoter%20stake%20sale%3A%20Sterling%20%26a