0case%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20happy%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20even%20though%20it%20took%20many%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20We%20have%20got%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%2C%20who%20is%20a%20wage%20labourer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20family%20had%20to%20sell%20between%20200%20and%20300%20yards%20of%20land%20to%20sustain%20the%20long%20and%20arduous%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20%3Cem%3Emazdoor%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BHindi%20for%20labourer%5D.%20We%20have%20only%20three%20or%20four%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20of%20land.%20To%20attend%20the%20court%20hearings%2C%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20aside%20my%20work%20for%20the%20day.%20We%20had%20to%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20to%20fight%20this%2C%20but%20by%20god%E2%80%99s%20grace%2C%20we%20have%20got%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasim%20earned%20a%20living%20by%20selling%20goats%20in%20local%20markets%20and%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamaydeen%2C%20who%20was%20in%20his%20farm%20gathering%20fodder%20for%20cattle%2C%20witnessed%20the%20mob%20chase%20Qasim%20towards%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12203951%2FSamaydeen.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12203951%2FSamaydeen.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12203951%2FSamaydeen-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701377%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESamaydeen%20survived%20the%20assault.%20Photo