title%22%3A%22Sons%20Of%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20In%20Congress'%202nd%20List%20For%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20announced%20a%20second%20list%20of%2043%20candidates%20for%20five%20states%20--%20Assam%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20one%20seat%20of%20the%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20Union%20Territory.%20Prominent%20among%20the%20candidates%20are%20GenNext%20leaders%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Tarun%20Gogoi%3B%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20in%20power%2C%20its%20government%20helmed%20by%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20crashed%20in%202016.%C2%A0%20The%20party%20currently%20has%20three%20MPs%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20the%20Congress's%20deputy%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20Jorhat%20--%20a%20change%20from%20the%20Kaliabor%20constituency%20he%20has%20been%20representing%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Koliabor%20constituency%20was%20absorbed%20into%20the%20Kaziranga%20seat%20during%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20the%20state.%20Sources%20said%20Mr%20Gogoi%20had%20preferred%20to%20shift%20to%20Jorhat%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20home%20constituency%20of%20his%20late%20father%20Tarun%20Gogoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENakul%20Nath%2C%20who%20was%20rumoured%20to%20be%20joining%20the%20BJP%20after%20his%20father%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief's%20post%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20again%20from%20Chhindwara%2C%20the%20constituency%20he%20currently%20represents.%20Nath%20senior%2C%2077%2C%20has%20said%20he%20would%20not%20contest%20elections%20any%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20was%20routed%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20state%20election%20held%20last%20year%20and%20has%20been%20having%20trouble%20holding%20its%20flock%20together.%20Among%20its%2010%20candidates%20in%20this%20list%20are%20two%20prominent%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamleshwar%20Patel%2C%20candidate%20from%20Sidhi%20and%20Omkar%20Singh%20Markam%2C%20candidate%20from%20the%20ST%20seat%20of%20Mandla%2C%20were%20both%20ministers%20in%20Kamal%20Nath's%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%20--%20the%20heartland%20state%20the%20Congress%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20last%20year%20--%20the%20party%20has%20announced%2010%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20will%20fight%20from%20Jalore%2C%20had%20lost%20the%20election%20from%20Jodhput%20to%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20in%202019.%20This%20time%2C%20several%20surveys%20were%20conducted%20before%20he%20chose%20a%20new%20constituency.%20Jalore%20is%20adjacent%20to%20his%20hometown%20Jodhpur.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20state's%20former%20police%20chief%20Harish%20Meena%20will%20contest%20from%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur.%20Rahul%20Kaswa%2C%20who%20crossed%20over%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20will%20contest%20from%20Churu%20and%20Brijendra%20Ola%20from%20Jhunjhunu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20list%20has%20also%20been%20chosen%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20caste%20arithmetic.%20Betting%20on%20Rahul%20Kaswa%2C%20who%20crossed%20over%20after%20being%20denied%20ticket%20is%20also%20good%20politics%2C%20party%20leaders%20maintain.%20Mr%20Kaswa%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20grassroots%20politicians%20and%20is%20deeply%20connected%20to%20his%20constituency%20Churu.%20The%20BJP%20had%20dropped%20him%20and%20fielded%20para-Olympian%20Devendra%20Jhajharia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20had%20been%20counting%20on%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasara%20leading%20from%20the%20front%20and%20contesting%20in%20this%20election.%20But%20the%20party%20brass%20has%20decided%20to%20play%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20party%20has%20fielded%20two%20sitting%20MLAs%20and%20a%20former%20legislator.%20two-term%20Congress%20legislator%20from%20Vav%20constituency%2C%20Geniben%20Thakor%2C%20will%20contest%20from%20Banaskantha%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20north%20Gujarat%20against%20BJP's%20Rekhaben%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20MLA%20Anant%20Patel%20--%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20from%20Vansda%20seat%20--%20will%20contest%20from%20Valsad%2C%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20MLA%20Lalit%20Vasoya%20will%20contest%20from%20Porbandar%20Lok%20Sabha%20sea%2C%20which%20he%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20second%20list%20was%20announced%20a%20day%20after%20the%20party's%20central%20election%20committee%2C%20chaired%20by%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20met%20to%20finalise%20the%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20discussions%20were%20held%20for%20more%20than%2060%20seats%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20and%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Daman%20and%20Diu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20announced%20today%20include%2013%20from%20Assam%2C%2010%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%2010%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20seven%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20three%20from%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710255000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fn8tksojg_congress-cec_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaurav-gogoi-vaibhav-gehlot-nakul-nath-in-congresss-2nd-list-for-lok-sabha-polls-5225188%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20Nakul%20Nath%20In%20Congress's%202nd%20List%20For%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaurav-gogoi-vaibhav-gehlot-nakul-nath-in-congresss-2nd-list-for-lok-sabha-polls-5225188%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaurav-gogoi-vaibhav-gehlot-nakul-nath-in-congresss-2nd-list-for-lok-sabha-polls-5225188%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaurav-gogoi-vaibhav-gehlot-nakul-nath-in-congresss-2nd-list-for-lok-sabha-polls-5225188%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Another%20Haryana%20Shocker%2C%20BJP%20Drops%20Senior%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%20From%20Cabinet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20attempt%20to%20fight%20anti-incumbency%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20it%20has%20ruled%20since%202014%2C%20has%20seen%20another%20big%20name%20being%20dropped.%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20arguably%20the%20best-known%20leader%20from%20the%20Haryana%20BJP%20after%20now%20former%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20has%20not%20found%20a%20place%20in%20the%20new%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20other%20ministers%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20Mr%20Khattar's%20cabinet%2C%20took%20oath%20with%20Mr%20Saini%20at%20a%20swiftly%20organised%20ceremony%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20entire%20cabinet%20resigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20omission%20of%20Mr%20Vij%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Haryana%20home%20minister%2C%20was%20even%20more%20surprising%20because%20there%20was%20speculation%20that%20he%20would%20be%20one%20of%20two%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20appointed%20by%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%20post%20was%20vacated%20by%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20of%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20left%20the%20legislature%20party%20meeting%2C%20where%20Mr%20Saini%20was%20picked%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20mid-way.%20Sources%20said%20he%20was%20visibly%20angry%20when%20he%20left%20the%20meeting%20-%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20central%20observers%20Agriculture%20Mini