t%20give%20me%20work%20for%20being%20friendly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108428587%2Cimgsize-458674.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fneha-dhupia-just-because-im-not-friendly-with-someone-it-doesnt-mean-that-they-dont-call-me-for-work-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F108428208.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108428208.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENeha%20Dhupia%20Bedi%20reflects%20on%20her%20multifaceted%20career%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20discussing%20her%20journey%2C%20memorable%20experiences%2C%20friendships%2C%20and%20the%20challenges%20of%20balancing%20work%20and%20family.%20She%20also%20shares%20personal%20insights%20into%20her%20approach%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20mother%2C%20and%20individual.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tejashree%20Bhopatkar%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fneha-dhupia-just-because-im-not-friendly-with-someone-it-doesnt-mean-that-they-dont-call-me-for-work-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F108428208.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heavy%20Rains%20Coupled%20With%20%26quot%3BPseudo-Development%26quot%3B%20And%20Govt%20Neglect%20Wrecks%20Havoc%20In%20Balochistan's%20Gwadar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180043%2F429664226_726364946296535_389126-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EKarachi%3A%20In%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%2C%20Gwadar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20port%20city%20on%20the%20southwestern%20coast%20of%20Balochistan%20%E2%80%94%20was%20ravaged%20by%20heavy%20rains%20leading%20to%20widespread%20destruction.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1818078%5C%22%3Eauthorities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%20the%20coastal%20town%20received%20180%20millimeters%20of%20rainfall%20over%20two%20days%20resulting%20in%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20were%20active%20to%20an%20extent%20only%20in%20the%20main%20city%20of%20Gwadar%20and%20in%20areas%20that%20were%20more%20affected%20such%20as%20Old%20Gwadar%20city%2C%20Jiwani%2C%20Pishukan%2C%20Surbandar%2C%20Palleri%2C%20Ganz%2C%20Kantani%2C%20and%20others%20where%20locals%20were%20living%20under%20the%20open%20sky.%20Affected%20people%2C%20however%2C%20had%20not%20been%20rescued%20and%20were%20left%20to%20manage%20on%20their%20own%20in%20other%20areas%20despite%20local%20administration%20declaring%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Gwadar%20is%20often%20showcased%20as%20a%20developed%20city%20by%20the%20local%20Pakistani%20media.%20It%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20changing%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20a%20sharp%20contrast%2C%20the%20cries%20of%20the%20Balochs%20grew%20louder%20amidst%20the%20heavy%20rains%2C%20raising%20questions%20on%20who%20will%20change%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20Baloch%2C%20a%20prominent%20activist%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20Gwadars%3A%20one%20portrayed%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20media%20as%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%2C%20and%20another%20Gwadar%20where%20locals%20are%20submerged%20in%20rain-flood%20water%20and%20struggling%20for%20drinking%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20how%20the%20recent%20rains%20have%20devastated%20the%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20noted%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Chouse%E2%80%9D%20means%20a%20single%20room%20in%20Gwadar%2C%20not%20the%20general%20definition%20of%20a%20house%20and%20it%20costs%20a%20huge%20amount%20to%20an%20individual%20to%20even%20construct%20and%20re-construct%20such%20a%20%E2%80%9Chouse%E2%80%9D%20when%20rain%20damages%20it%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20shelter%2C%20the%20ancient%20fishing%20community%20in%20the%20city%20has%20also%20been%20severely%20affected.%20Their%20boats%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lifeline%20for%20them%20as%20they%20rely%20on%20them%20for%20their%20livelihood%20%E2%80%94%20are%20damaged%2C%20each%20cost%20about%20Pakistani%20Rupee%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20boats%20have%20been%20damaged%20and%20some%20of%20them%20swept%20away%20by%20heavy%20rains%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20affected%20fishermen%20to%20Mahrang.%20She%20continued%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20the%20local%20administration%20had%20announced%20a%20high%20alter%20and%20warned%20them%20strictly%2C%20the%20fishermen%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20save%20their%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20is%20the%20real%20culprit%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20devastating%20flood%20hit%20Pakistan%20which%20resulted%20in%20severe%20destruction%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Sindh%20and%20Balochistan%20provinces.%20Gwadar%20also%20witnessed%20torrential%20rains%20followed%20by%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20journalist%20Behram%20Baloch%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRains%20or%20miseries%20are%20not%20first-time%20occurrences%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20Balochs%C2%A0%20nor%20are%20heavy%20rains%20new%20to%20Gwadar.%20Even%20in%202008%20and%202010%2C%20such%20rainstorms%20severally%20hit%20Gwadar.%20Ever%20since%20the%20government%20has%20not%20developed%20any%20infrastructure%20or%20drainage%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20interesting%20point%20is%20that%20recent%20rains%20have%20badly%20exposed%20the%20state%20and%20its%20claims%20regarding%20development%20projects%20in%20Gwadar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701333%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20Baloch%20along%20with%20affected%20families%20in%20Gwadar.%20Photo%3A%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Gwadar%20resident%2C%20went%20door%20to%20door%20to%20meet%20the%20affected%20people%20during%20the%20recent%20crisis.%20She%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo-mega%20development%20projects%E2%80%9D%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20ruin%20and%20destruction%20of%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20climate%20crisis%20is%20a%20reality%2C%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20negligence%20made%20it%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20when%20she%20met%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20they%20told%20her%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20Chine-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20that%20has%20ruined%20our%20lives%2C%20stolen%20our%20employment%2C%20and%20now%20destroyed%20our%20homes.%20The%20rain%20has%20done%20less%20damage%20than%20CPEC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20pointed%20out%20that%20infrastructure%20development%20has%20altered%20natural%20the%20drainage%20patterns%2C%20which%20previously%20facilitated%20the%20drainage%20of%20rain-flood%20water.%20Further%2C%20she%20asserted%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo%20projects%E2%80%9D%20have%20now%20obstructed%20natural%20pathways%20and%20have%20failed%20to%20assist%20in%20draining%20rain-flood%20water.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20some%20point%2C%20the%20locals%20even%20broke%20the%20roads%20to%20alleviate%20flooding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20is%20inactive%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20those%20who%20initiate%20the%20relief%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20less%20active%20in%20Gwadar%2C%20where%20a%20small%20number%20of%20locals%2C%20NGOs%20and%20other%20activists%20are%20voluntarily%20working%20in%20the%20city.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20that%20organisations%20like%20the%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20which%20are%20active%20in%20relief%20work%20are%20facing%20threats.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20relief%20camp%20in%20Hub%2C%20a%20city%20of%20Balochistan%2C%20was%20removed%20and%20volunteers%20were%20warned%20not%20to%20continue%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20local%20administration%E2%80%99s%20presence%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20mentioned%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20seen%20them%E2%80%9D.%20She%20claimed%C2%A0%20that%20officials%20came%20and%20took%20pictures%20with%20generators%20to%20pretend%20that%20they%20were%20helping%20locals%20even%20when%20the%20localities%20only%C2%A0%20brought%20generators%20to%20pump%20out%20floodwater.%20The%20locals%20were%20afraid%20of%20speaking%20as%20they%20are%20under%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20military%20forces.%20%E2%80%9CLocals%20have%20been%20scrutinised%2C%20but%20no%20one%20is%20coming%20forward%20to%20help%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20similar%20views%2C%20Behram%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20active%20this%20time%20like%20how%20they%20remained%20inactive%20during%20the%202010%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20inactivity%20is%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20compel%20locals%20to%20leave%20their%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20stated%20that%20the%20torrential%20rains%20have%20revealed%20every%20unkind%20plan%20of%20the%20state%20towards%20Balochs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gwadar%2C%20locals%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20even%20fishing%20community%20faces%20restrictions%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20fish%20freely.%20Now%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20silent%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20affected%20people%2C%20indicating%20that%20locals%20will%20ultimately%20be%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20land.%20She%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20you%20lack%20shelter%20and%20protection%20for%20work%2C%20you%20are%20left%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20make%20a%20difficult%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20a%20Gwadar%20where%20we%20can%20have%20two%20meals%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20affected%20people%20told%20Mahrang%2C%20she%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehram%20recalled%20an%20event%20during%20his%20reporting%20between%202004%20and%202005%20when%20official%20authorities%20were%20considering%20the%20relocation%20of%20entire%20local%20population%20to%20another%20place.%20However%2C%20this%20plan%20was%20later%20withheld%20due%20to%20the%20difficulty%20of%20relocating%20such%20a%20large%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20inactivity%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20they%20want%20locals%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20so%20they%20can%20install%20their%20mega%20projects%20in%20Gwadar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunds%20should%20be%20monitored%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1819513%2Fpm-unveils-relief-package-for-calamity-hit-gwadar%5C%22%3Evisited%3C%2Fa%3E%20rain-hit%20Gwadar%2C%20unveiling%20a%20relief%20package%20for%20affected%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20people%20do%20not%20need%20just%20a%20sack%20of%20wheat%2C%20or%20empty%20relief%20package%20announcements%2C%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20assistance%20should%20aim%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives%2C%20to%20provide%20them%20basic%20needs.%20But%2C%20politicians%20only%20show%20up%20when%20people%20are%20devastated%2C%20because%20we%20know%20what%20they%20have%20done%20in%20previous%20disasters%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr.%20Mahrang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urged%20international%20communities%20to%20monitor%20funds%20being%20given%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20directly%20approach%20the%20affected%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180043%2F429664226_726364946296535_389126-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fheavy-rains-coupled-with-pseudo-development-and-govt-neglect-wrecks-havoc-in-pakistans-gwadar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Gwadar%2C%20locals%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20even%20fishing%20community%20faces%20restrictions%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20fish%20freely.%20Now%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20silent%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20affected%20people%2C%20indicating%20that%20locals%20will%20ultimately%20be%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fheavy-rains-coupled-with-pseudo-development-and-govt-neglect-wrecks-havoc-in-pakistans-gwadar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Suffers%20Artery%20Rupture%20After%20He%20Falls%20At%20Engagement%20Party%2C%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20tragic%20incident%20occurred%20in%20Western%20Australia%2C%20where%20Liam%20Trimmer%2C%20a%20British%20police%20officer%20residing%20in%20Australia%2C%20died%20following%20an%20unforeseen%20mishap.%20Mr%20Trimmer%2C%20who%20was%20celebrating%20his%20engagement%20with%20his%20fiancee%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20reportedly%20slipped%20and%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20cutting%20open%20his%20carotid%20artery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carotid%20arteries%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20supplying%20blood%20to%20the%20brain.%20Despite%20efforts%20from%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20intervene%20and%20save%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20he%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20before%20emergency%20services%20could%20reach%20the%20scene%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68541139%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColleagues%20said%20the%20senior%20constable%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20officer%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Bloved%20helping%20his%20community%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20the%20police%20officer%20fell%20and%20suffered%20the%20fatal%20neck%20wound%2C%20which%20has%20prompted%20an%20inquest%20to%20be%20opened%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Faustralasia%2Faustralia-british-man-death-freak-accident-b2511080.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20done%20to%20try%20and%20save%20him%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20to%20be%20and%20I%20know%20everyone%20that%20was%20involved%20is%20hurting%20at%20the%20moment%20and%20I%20think%20they%20wish%20they%20could%20just%20wake%20up%20from%20this%20nightmare%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commissioner%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.9news.com.au%2Fnational%2Fwestern-australia-police-officer-dies-in-serious-accident%2F94592b25-7283-404d-b94b-8a64db3ea1e2%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%209News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20extraordinary%20officer%20loved%20helping%20the%20community%20and%20was%20a%20fine%20example%20of%20WA%20%5BWestern%20Australia%5D%20policing%20and%20it's%20just%20such%20a%20tragedy.%20%5BHe%5D%20a%20very%2C%20very%20confident%2C%20capable%20young%20man%20with%20his%20whole%20life%20ahead%20of%20him%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20sad%20this%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20Western%20Australian%20Police%20Union%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20passing%20of%20a%20valued%20member%20of%20the%20blue%20family%20deeply%20saddened%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20WA%20Police%20Union%20sends%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20colleagues%20of%20the%20fallen%20officer%20during%20this%20difficult%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FWAPoliceUnion%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02KEFndeYZFfjKnFZTG5X6sGV9kC4JK81gVcZpxfjTiHgAJiogSRVyj1MkYCqnsFosl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Mr%20Trimmer%20moved%20to%20Australia%20and%20completed%20his%20training%20at%20the%20Joondalup%20Police%20Academy.%20Following%20this%2C%20he%20transitioned%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Kalgoorlie.%20Within%20the%20force%2C%20he%20became%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Gang%20Crime%20Squad%20and%20the%20tactical%20response%20group%2C%20emerging%20as%20a%20respected%20local%20community%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribed%20by%20local%20media%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bposter%20boy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20force%2C%20he%20was%20known%20to%20have%20inspired%20other%20young%20UK%20citizens%20to%20make%20the%20move%20to%20Western%20Australia%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20his%20appearance%20on%20the%20BBC%20series%20%26quot%3BWanted%20Down%20Under%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20delves%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20prospective%20migrants.%20The%20state's%20police%20union%20also%20extended%20its%20condolences.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7rggvs5_liam-trimmer_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suffers-artery-rupture-after-he-falls-at-engagement-party-dies-5225295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20efforts%20from%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20save%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20he%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20before%20emergency%20services%20could%20reach%20the%20scene.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suffers-artery-rupture-after-he-falls-at-engagement-party-dies-5225295%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suffers-artery-rupture-after-he-falls-at-engagement-party-dies-5225295%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-suffers-artery-rupture-after-he-falls-at-engagement-party-dies-5225295%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pehli%20Naukri%20Pakki'%20to%2030%20lakh%20Government%20Jobs%2C%20Congress%20Seizes%20the%20Right(s)%20Moment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F17182347%2F22.2.22-48.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20announced%20five%20major%20policy%20proposals%20to%20tackle%20youth%20unemployment%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%20Described%20as%20Yuva%20Nyay%20Guarantees%2C%20these%20include%20a%20clear%20timeline%20to%20fill%20vacant%20posts%20in%20the%20central%20government%3B%20a%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%2C%20gig%20workers%E2%80%99%20social%20security%2C%20a%20startup%20fund%2C%20and%20curbing%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20scrap%20the%20Agniveer%20Scheme%2C%20a%20four-year%20tour%20of%20duty%20contract%20for%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20array%20of%20promises%20and%20guarantees%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20space%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20appropriate.%20Congress%20guarantees%20draw%20upon%20the%20guarantees%20promised%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20legal%20guarantees%20quite%20different%20from%20BJP%20guarantees%2C%20which%20are%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20commitments%20and%20assurances.%20While%20constantly%20mocking%20Congress%20guarantee%20schemes%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20state%20elections%20claiming%20that%20it%20would%20bankrupt%20the%20exchequer%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20embrace%20the%20word%20guarantee%20after%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20Karnataka%20elections.%20Congress%20guarantees%20contributed%2C%20at%20least%20partially%2C%20to%20its%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20also%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20BJP%20started%20using%20the%20term%20guarantee%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20context%20for%20these%20proposals%20is%20the%20underwhelming%20economic%20performance%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20marked%20by%20its%20stark%20failure%20to%20address%20two%20related%20challenges.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20unequal%20distribution%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20rapid%20economic%20growth%2C%20which%20have%20accrued%20predominantly%20to%20the%20top%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20income%20earners%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20economic%20inequality%2C%20has%20shown%20an%20alarming%20increase.%20The%20second%20challenge%20is%20high%20unemployment%2C%20which%20reached%20a%2045-year%20high%20in%202017.%20According%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20of%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%20unemployment%20rate%20was%2045.4%25%20for%202022-23%2C%20six%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20overall%20unemployment%20rate%20of%207.5%25.%20The%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20for%20July%E2%80%93September%202023%20showed%20that%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20youth%20in%20urban%20India%20was%2017.3%25%2C%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20official%20overall%20unemployment%20rate%20of%206.6%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20foregrounds%20unemployment%20and%20livelihood%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20proposals%20acknowledge%20the%20centrality%20of%20unemployment%20and%20joblessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20has%20figured%20prominently%20in%20the%20second%20leg%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra.%20Given%20its%20timing%20and%20given%20its%20emphasis%20on%20Nyaya%20(justice)%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20would%20be%20assessed%20for%20its%20attempts%20to%20respond%20to%20specific%20political%20issues%2C%20and%20not%20just%20abstract%20rhetoric.%20The%20announcement%20of%20five%20guarantees%20is%20a%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%20The%20idea%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20governments%20can%20improve%20conditions%20of%20life%20and%20work%20for%20their%20citizens%20by%20providing%20employment%20and%20public%20services%2C%20which%20too%20can%20generate%20employment%2C%20and%20not%20just%20by%20simply%20distributing%20cash%20and%20rations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701320%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOn%2017%20September%20Youth%20gathered%20to%20celebrate%20the%20birthday%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20%E2%80%98National%20Unemployment%20Day%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20protest%20against%20wrong%20policies%20of%20government%2C%20unemployment%20and%20contract%20system%20in%20jobs.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FPrajjwal3959%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20central%20ideological%20plank%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%202024%20elections%20is%20social%20justice.%20While%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20raised%20the%20issues%20of%20political%20authoritarianism%20and%20socio-economic%20discrimination%2C%20its%20second%20edition%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20is%20geared%20to%20achieve%20the%20constitutional%20ideals%20of%20political%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20justice.%20Political%20justice%20entails%20promoting%20the%20constitutional%20values%20of%20dignity%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20Indians%3B%20social%20justice%20involves%20participation%20of%20marginalised%20sections%20in%20decision-making%2C%20unity%20and%20harmony)%3B%20and%20economic%20justice%20entails%20a%20job%20for%20every%20Indian%20youth%2C%20and%20ending%20inequality.%20These%20are%20the%20key%20planks%20of%20this%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPehli%20Naukri%20Pakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(first%20job%20guaranteed)%20which%20is%20the%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%20is%20an%20important%20guarantee%20to%20tackle%20unemployment.%20It%20will%20be%20like%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20that%20gave%20legally%20guaranteed%20employment%20to%20lakhs%20of%20people%20on%20demand%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20proposed%20Right%20to%20Apprenticeship%20law%2C%20will%20mandate%20private%20or%20public%20sector%20concerns%20to%20provide%20a%20one-year%20internship%20with%20part-government%20funding%20to%20any%20college%20degree%2Fdiploma%20holder%20on%20demand%20along%20with%20Rs%208500%20monthly%20stipend.%20This%20is%20for%20one%20year%20but%20it%20will%20provide%20skills%20that%20can%20facilitate%20employment%20in%20the%20future.%20Bharti%20Bharosa%2C%20a%20promise%20to%20fill%2030%20lakh%20vacancies%20in%20government%20sector%20jobs%2C%20is%20a%20really%20big%20guarantee.%20Another%203%20lakh%20jobs%20could%20be%20created%20in%20the%20education%20and%20health%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20like%20Anganwadi%20and%20ASHA%20workers%20and%20the%20educational%20and%20health%20institutions%20of%20the%20central%20government.%20Then%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20proposal%20to%20establish%20a%20Rs.%205%2C000%20crore%20national%20fund%20to%20fund%20to%20youth%20across%20districts.%20People%20below%2040%20years%20of%20age%20will%20be%20able%20to%20avail%20of%20this%20fund.%20Promising%20a%20law%20for%20social%20security%20for%20gig%20workers%20such%20as%20drivers%2C%20guards%20and%20delivery%20boys%20is%20another%20important%20guarantee.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20paper%20leaks%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20will%20standardise%20the%20government%20recruitment%20exam%20process%20and%20%E2%80%98stop%20its%20outsourcing%E2%80%99.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20a%20legally%20guaranteed%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP).%20For%20the%20first%20time%20a%20national%20party%20has%20supported%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20legally%20guaranteed%20MSP%2C%20which%20is%20a%20guaranteed%20floor%20price%20for%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20called%20its%20promises%20as%20Congress%20guarantees%20but%20the%20BJP%20calls%20them%20Modi%20Guarantee%20or%20Modi%20Sarkar%20ki%20Guarantee.%20The%20latter%20are%20essentially%20government%20funded%20programmes%20and%20schemes%20across%20sectors%20which%20have%20been%20named%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20renamed%20as%20Modi%20ki%20Guarantee.%20These%20guarantees%20depend%20for%20their%20implementation%20on%20trust%20in%20the%20leader%20or%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20himself%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98people%20trust%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20because%20all%20other%20parties%20make%20false%20promises%E2%80%99.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20means%20he%20alone%20could%20fulfill%20them.%20These%20are%20not%20legal%20guarantees%20or%20rights%2C%20they%20are%20assurances%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20ease%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20business%2C%20and%20health%20etc.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20many%20of%20the%20economic%20promises%20made%20by%20this%20government%20over%20the%20past%20ten%20years%20remain%20unfulfilled%20as%20shown%20by%20status%20update%20of%20the%20major%20guarantees.%20The%20Congress%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20claims%20that%20more%20than%20four%20crore%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20guarantee%20schemes%20in%20Karnataka%20since%20the%20election%20of%20its%20government%20last%20summer.%20This%20will%20be%20its%20poll%20plank%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%20in%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20foregrounded%20employment%20and%20livelihood%20as%20major%20issues%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20for%20the%20general%20election.%20But%20much%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20these%20issues%20are%20communicated%20and%20whether%20the%20messages%20can%20reach%20people%20and%20whether%20it%20can%20surpass%20emotional%20issues%2C%20especially%20those%20surrounding%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20guarantees%20will%20be%20evaluated%20for%20the%20political%20and%20electoral%20dividends%20rather%20they%20can%20yield%20than%20effectiveness%20as%20policy%20measures.%20But%20irrespective%20of%20outcomes%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20are%20notable%20in%20terms%20of%20shifting%20public%20attention%20back%20on%20the%20urgency%20of%20policies%20to%20deal%20with%20unemployment%20and%20the%20problems%20of%20those%20facing%20distress%20and%20destitution.%20The%20basic%20principle%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20guarantee%20all%20citizens%20a%20decent%20life%20and%20a%20minimum%20standard%20of%20living%20is%20one%20that%20definitely%20should%20be%20supported.%20In%20this%20sense%2C%20it%20goes%20beyond%20the%20immediate%20impact%20that%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20economic%20guarantees%20may%20have%20on%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20emphasis%20they%20give%20to%20education%2C%20health%20and%20employment%20%3Cem%3Eas%20rights%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20can%20promote%20a%20deeper%20transformation%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EZoya%20Hasan%20is%20Professor%20Emerita%2C%20Centre%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F17182347%2F22.2.22-48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpehli-naukri-pakki-to-30-lakh-government-jobs-congress-seizes-the-rights-moment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20space%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20appropriate.%20Congress%20guarantees%20draw%20upon%20the%20guarantees%20it%20promised%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Rajasthan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpehli-naukri-pakki-to-30-lakh-government-jobs-congress-seizes-the-rights-moment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20BJP%20Went%20For%2011th%20Hour%20Change%20In%20Haryana.%20The%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20Link%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20towing%20a%20fine%20line%20in%20Haryana%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20sending%20multiple%20messages%20through%20the%20change%20in%20in%20the%20top%20post.%20Sources%20said%20the%20change%20made%20it%20necessary%20for%20the%20whole%20cabinet%20--%20including%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20of%20JJP%C2%A0%20to%20resign%20--%20which%20was%20what%20the%20party%20was%20aiming%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20JJP%20(Jannayak%20Janata%20Party)%20had%20fallen%20out%20over%20seat%20sharing%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20contest%20all%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20JJP%2C%20which%20failed%20to%20win%20any%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20wanted%20at%20least%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20acrimonious%20break-up%20with%20JJP%20or%20sacking%20of%20Mr%20Chautala%20from%20the%20cabinet%20would%20have%20sent%20a%20wrong%20message%20to%20Jats%2C%20a%20substantial%20chunk%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20chose%20to%20take%20a%20roundabout%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20set%20of%20message%20was%20sent%20through%20the%20choice%20of%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Nayab%20Saini%2C%20a%20strong%20leader%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20castes%2C%20to%20fill%20the%20shoes%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20--%20one%20that%20showed%20the%20party%20supporting%20the%20non-Jats%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20Birendra%20Singh's%20son%20and%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Hisar%20Brijendra%20Chaudhary%20joining%20the%20Congress%20last%20week%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20this%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20Haryana's%20population%20are%20Jats%2C%20the%20rest%20belong%20to%20other%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Kurukshetra%2C%20will%20take%20oath%20at%205%20pm%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Khattar%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20possibly%20from%20Kurukshetra%2C%20the%20seat%20Mr%20Saini%20is%20vacating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20will%20be%20held%20on%20time%20--%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20hold%20simultaneous%20polls%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5cf09j2o_nayab-singh-saini_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-went-for-11th-hour-change-in-haryana-the-dushyant-chautala-link-5224791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20towing%20a%20fine%20line%20in%20Haryana%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20sending%20multiple%20messages%20through%20the%20change%20in%20in%20the%20top%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-went-for-11th-hour-change-in-haryana-the-dushyant-chautala-link-5224791%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjp-w