3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108438247.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20European%20Parliament%20is%20suing%20the%20European%20Union's%20executive%20over%20unblocking%20funds%20to%20Hungary%20while%20Hungary%20was%20blocking%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%20The%20lawsuit%20aims%20to%20establish%20clarity%20on%20the%20link%20between%20EU%20funds%20and%20democracy.%20The%20outcome%20will%20determine%20if%20Hungary%20has%20to%20return%20the%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Flawmakers-set-to-sue-eu-leaders-for-horse-trading-with-funds-to-hungary%2Farticleshow%2F108438247.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Flawmakers-set-to-sue-eu-leaders-for-horse-trading-with-funds-to-hungary%2Famp_articleshow%2F108438247.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Flawmakers-set-to-sue-eu-leaders-for-horse-trading-with-funds-to-hungary%2Famp_articleshow%2F108438247.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin's%20Cryptic%20Post%20On%20Rahane's%20Batting%20During%20Ranji%20Final%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20social%20media%20post%20on%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E's%20batting%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Vidarbha%20has%20gone%20viral.%20Rahane%20survived%20an%20extremely%20close%20LBW%20appeal%20as%20a%20delivery%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umesh%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1258-umesh-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20seamed%20back%20and%20crashed%20into%20his%20pads.%20Although%20Vidarbha%20were%20extremely%20confident%2C%20the%20umpire%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20batter%20and%20replays%20showed%20that%20it%20would%20have%20been%20umpire's%20call.%20The%20commentators%20remarked%20that%20Rahane%20misread%20the%20line%20of%20the%20delivery%20resulting%20in%20some%20discomfort%20and%20Ashwin%20also%20highlighted%20a%20similar%20concern%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20talk%20about%20Ajinkya%20Rahane's%20head%20position.%20When%20the%20head%20falls%20over%2C%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20to%20play%20deliveries%20that%20cut%20in.%20When%20your%20head%20falls%20over%2C%20the%20delivery%20that%20seams%20in%20will%20always%20trouble%20you.%20Ajinkya%20will%20have%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20the%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20commentator%20said%20following%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Bengal%20cricketer%20Joydeep%20Mukherjee%20also%20noticed%20on%20commentary%20that%20Rahane's%20foot%20position%20gave%20the%20expression%20that%20he%20expected%20the%20ball%20to%20come%20straight%20to%20his%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fn3d807j8_s_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20foot%20pointing%20towards%20mid-off%20tells%20me%20that%20he%20was%20playing%20for%20the%20ball%20going%20straight%20and%20not%20jagging%20back%20otherwise%20it%20would%20be%20a%20lot%20straighter.%20Because%20of%20the%20length%20he%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20adjust%20the%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mukherjee%20said.%3C%2Fp