ia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108438033.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20Ugandan%20court%20has%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20by%20LGBT%20advocacy%20group%20Sexual%20Minorities%20Uganda%20(SMUG)%20seeking%20government%20registration%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bundesirable%26quot%3B%20name.%20Same-sex%20relations%20are%20illegal%20in%20Uganda%2C%20and%20SMUG's%20operations%20are%20suspended%2C%20which%20could%20impact%20human%20rights%20for%20the%20LGBT%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fugandan-court-backs-governments-refusal-to-register-lgbt-organisation%2Farticleshow%2F108438033.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fugandan-court-backs-governments-refusal-to-register-lgbt-organisation%2Famp_articleshow%2F108438033.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fugandan-court-backs-governments-refusal-to-register-lgbt-organisation%2Famp_articleshow%2F108438033.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine-based%20groups%20claim%20raids%20into%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710247133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12263%2Fproduction%2F_132893347_russia_legion_grab.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68541911%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian%20rebel%20forces%20claim%20villages%20in%20Kursk%20and%20Belgorod%20areas%20-%20Moscow%20says%20the%20attacks%20failed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A235%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68541911%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68541911.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68541911.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Contrasting%20Reactions%20to%20CAA%20in%20West%20Bengal%3A%20Matuas%20Celebrate%2C%20Rajbanshis%20Express%20Discontent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12171458%2FUntitled-design-38-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20has%20triggered%20varying%20reactions%20among%20communities%20across%20various%20districts%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20While%20Matua%20communities%20largely%20forming%20the%20Bangladeshi%20refugees%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20are%20expressing%20relief%20and%20excitement%2C%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20emerges%20in%20North%20Bengal%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20first%20public%20address%20after%20the%20CAA%20notification%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20termed%20the%20CAA%20a%20divisional%20tactic%20to%20partition%20Bengal%20again.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20become%20refugees%20again.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20bloodshed%20and%20people%20have%20come%20from%20Bangladesh.%20We%20are%20not%20accepting%20CAA.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20accept%20NRC%20and%20divisiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20at%20Habra%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20districts%20with%20significant%20Matua%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20second-largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20constituting%203.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20Matuas%20have%20persistently%20advocated%20for%20the%20proper%20rehabilitation%20of%20Hindu%20Bengali%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh.%20In%202019%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20secured%20victories%20in%20Matua-dominated%20seats%20like%20Ranaghat%20and%20Bangaon%20in%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20while%20narrowly%20losing%20Krishnanagar%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC).%20However%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20Panchayat%20election%2C%20TMC%20recovered%20its%20lost%20ground%20winning%2049%20out%20of%20the%2053%20panchayats%20in%20these%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20won%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20eyeing%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Matua%20support%20again%20to%20retain%20its%20two%20seats%2C%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20on%20Monday%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20recent%20announcement.%20In%20the%20Matua-dominated%20areas%20of%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024Parganas%2C%20the%20BJP%20workers%20organised%20celebratory%20events%20to%20commemorate%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20political%20victory.%20Shantanu%20Thakur%2C%20the%20junior%20Union%20minister%20and%20head%20of%20All%20India%20Matua%20Mahasangha%2C%20hurried%20to%20the%20state%20BJP%20office%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20presenting%20packets%20of%20sweets%20to%20commemorate%20what%20he%20deemed%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20event.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Thakur%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistory%20has%20been%20created%20today.%20A%20century%20from%20now%2C%20the%20government%20may%20change%2C%20but%20no%20one%20will%20ever%20question%20the%20citizenship%20of%20refugees.%20This%20is%20a%20response%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20who%20spread%20misinformation%20and%20created%20unnecessary%20panic%20about%20the%20CAA%20jeopardising%20individuals%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20strategically%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20the%20interests%20of%20lower-caste%20Hindus%2C%20aiming%20to%20unite%20their%20votes.%20The%20party%20has%20successfully%20gained%20influence%20within%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20two%20significant%20Scheduled%20Caste%20communities%2C%20namely%20the%20Rajbanshi%20and%20Namashudra%20groups%2C%20collectively%20accounting%20for%2018.35%25%20and%2017.41%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20total%20Scheduled%20Caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscontent%20among%20Rajbanshis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%2C%20asserting%20their%20indigenous%20status%2C%20vehemently%20opposes%20the%20CAA%2C%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20instead.%20The%20BJP%2C%20a%20dominant%20political%20force%20in%20the%20region%2C%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20mitigating%20discontent%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanshi%20Badan%20Barman%2C%20a%20prominent%20leader%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20Language%20Academy%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20CAA%2C%20we%20want%20NRC.%20If%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20enforce%20CAA%20here%2C%20it%20must%20first%20engage%20in%20dialogue%20with%20the%20people%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20We%20want%20NRC%20with%20a%20cut-off%20date%20of%20March%2025%2C%201971.%20Rajbanshis%20are%20not%20ignorant%20anymore.%20We%20will%20only%20support%20those%20who%20address%20our%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Roy%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kamtapur%20Party%2C%20echoed%20this%20sentiment%2C%20expressing%20concern%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20Kamtapuri%20community.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20Kamtapuris%20are%20natives%20of%20this%20place%2C%20and%20we%20strongly%20oppose%20the%20way%20CAA%20has%20been%20introduced%20without%20providing%20us%20any%20protection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajbanshis%2C%20making%20up%20around%2030%25%20of%20North%20Bengal%2C%20are%20the%20largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group%20in%20the%20state.%20For%20many%20years%20now%2C%20the%20community%20has%20been%20demanding%20territorial%20autonomy%20or%20separate%20statehood%20due%20to%20the%20perceived%20adverse%20effects%20of%20a%20significant%20influx%20of%20Bengali%20refugees%20from%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20land%2C%20economic%20opportunities%2C%20and%20cultural%20identity%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20both%20constituencies%20with%20over%2015%25%20Rajbanshi%20population.%20Rajbashis%20now%20find%20themselves%20disappointed%20and%20without%20the%20safeguards%20they%20had%20hoped%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharaja%20Anant%20Maharaj%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%2C%20a%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20had%20previously%20promised%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Kamtapur%20union%20territory.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20he%20has%20fallen%20silent%20on%20the%20matter.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20his%20reaction.%20The%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20CPI(M)%20minister%20criticised%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20approach%20as%20%E2%80%9Celection-centric%20drama%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20exploiting%20historical%20events%20to%20divide%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20to%20deliberately%20sow%20confusion%20among%20the%20residents.%20They%20already%20vote%2C%20receive%20rations%20and%20pay%20taxes.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20linking%20them%20to%20new%20citizenship%20policies%3F%20It%20reflects%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20political%20approach.%20Should%20the%20citizenship%20of%20even%20one%20person%20be%20jeopardized%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20protest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukhvilas%20Varma%2C%20former%20Congress%20MP%20of%20Cooch%20Behar%2C%20dismissed%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgimmick%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20playing%20a%20dangerous%20game%20of%20polarisation%20politics.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20claim%20that%20nobody%E2%80%99s%20citizenship%20will%20be%20revoked%2C%20but%20applicants%20must%20initiate%20the%20process%2C%20followed%20by%20providing%20documentary%20evidence.%20Now%2C%20the%20burden%20lies%20on%20the%20individual%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20country%20due%20to%20religious%20reasons%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20judgment.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20engaging%20in%20polarisation%20politics%20for%20long.%20Even%20TMC%20was%20party%20to%20its%20original%20CAA%20200C%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12171458%2FUntitled-design-38-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcontrasting-reactions-to-caa-in-west-bengal-matuas-celebrate-rajbanshis-express-discontent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Matua%20communities%20largely%20forming%20the%20Bangladeshi%20refugees%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20are%20expressing%20relief%20and%20excitement%2C%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20emerges%20in%20North%20Bengal%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcontrasting-reactions-to-caa-in-west-bengal-matuas-celebrate-rajbanshis-express-discontent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Missing%20skiers%20tried%20to%20dig%20'snow%20caves'%20before%20they%20died%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F70x70%2Fskynews-cantonal-police-valais_6487963.jpg%3F20240312124322%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmissing-skiers-attempted-