2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-a-travel-powerhouse-agoda-will-continue-accelerated-expansion-ceo-124031200723_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-a-travel-powerhouse-agoda-will-continue-accelerated-expansion-ceo-124031200723_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Mamata's%20Solo%20Act%20In%20West%20Bengal%20Is%20A%20Big%20Setback%20For%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqm3qh9ng_mamata-banerjee_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepeatedly-declared-desire-for-respectable-seat-sharing-congress-slams-trinamool-after-it-announces-candidates-5211679%5C%22%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20a%20jolt%20to%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%2C%20severed%20ties%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20announced%20that%20the%20party%20will%20go%20solo%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Putting%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-says-it-will-contest-all-42-bengal-seats-dashes-congress-hopes-5114885%5C%22%3Eend%20to%20all%20rumours%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20seat-sharing%2C%20the%20party%20announced%20candidates%20for%20all%2042%20parliamentary%20seats%20at%20its%20'Jon%20Gorjan%20Sabha'%20-%20'People's%20Roar%20Rally'%20-%20in%20Kolkata.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20has%20renominated%2016%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20has%20fielded%2012%20women.%20There%20are%20also%20some%20political%20novices%20and%20surprises%20on%20the%20list%2C%20including%20former%20cricketers%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20from%20Baharampur%20and%20Kirti%20Azad%20from%20Bardhaman-Durgapur.%20Both%20are%20'outsiders'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonths%20Of%20Friction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC's%20decision%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20visible%20friction%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20extended%20from%20confrontations%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-delayed-seat-sharing-discussions-trinamool-on-no-tie-up-4923482%5C%22%3Eslow%20pace%20of%20seat-sharing%3C%2Fa%3E%20talks%20to%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepeatedly-declared-desire-for-respectable-seat-sharing-congress-slams-trinamool-after-it-announces-candidates-5211679%5C%22%3EAdhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury's%3C%2Fa%3E%20persistent%20personal%20attacks%20against%20Mamata%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20grand%20old%20party's%20attitude%20towards%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20that%20the%20TMC%20saw%20as%20visible%20apathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20peeved%2C%20reacted%20strongly%20to%20the%20TMC's%20'unilateral'%20announcements.%20Its%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20repeatedly%20declared%20its%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20respectable%20seat-sharing%20agreement%20with%20the%20TMC%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20always%20maintained%20that%20such%20an%20agreement%20has%20to%20be%20finalised%20through%20negotiations%20and%20not%20by%20unilateral%20announcements.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20always%20wanted%20the%20INDIA%20group%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERift%20Over%20Seat-Sharing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20and%20Congress%20had%20been%20wrangling%20over%20seats%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months.%20Sources%20say%20initially%2C%20the%20TMC%20offered%20two%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20wanted%20at%20least%20six%20to%20eight.%20The%20TMC's%20contention%20was%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20only%20two%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20drew%20a%20blank%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20in%202021.%20The%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20was%20buoyed%20by%20its%20victory%20in%20the%20Sagardighi%20bypoll%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20hence%20was%20not%20up%20for%20a%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Chowdhury's%20Baharampur%20constituency%20was%20also%20not%20included%20in%20the%20two%20seats%20offered%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20further%20irked%20the%20state%20Congress%20unit.%20It%20convinced%20the%20central%20leadership%20that%20going%20by%20the%20Muslim%20votes%20the%20Congress%20won%20in%20the%20bypoll%2C%20the%20TMC%20should%20not%20ignore%20its%20demand%20for%20at%20least%20six%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutsiders%20And%20Local%20Biggies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC's%20nomination%20of%20former%20cricketer%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20from%20Baharampur%20constituency%2C%20which%20historically%20has%20been%20Chowdhury's%20stronghold%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20the%20Congress.%20Yet%2C%20provided%20BJP%20chooses%20to%20'go%20easy'%20on%20the%20seat%2C%20there%20are%20strong%20chances%20that%20Chowdhury%20may%20win%20the%20seat%20as%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20TMC.%20Moreover%2C%20Pathan%20is%20not%20from%20Bengal%2C%20and%20being%20a%20'%3Cem%3Ebohiragato%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(outsider)-the%20term%20was%20coined%20by%20the%20TMC%20to%20attack%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20previous%20elections-might%20work%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20field%20Mohammad%20Shami%20from%20the%20Basirhat%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20Incidentally%2C%20Shami%20plays%20for%20Bengal%20in%20the%20Ranji%20trophy.%20Though%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20give%20his%20consent%2C%20his%20candidature%20can%20give%20a%20much-needed%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20to%20the%20BJP%20as%20Muslim%20youth%20may%20rally%20around%20him.%20The%20TMC%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20has%20been%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20in%20the%20Basirhat%20constituency%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-whos-sheikh-shahjahan-trinamool-strongman-at-centre-of-sandeshkali-row-5080238%5C%22%3ESandeskhali%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaga.%20It%20was%20to%20salvage%20the%20situation%20that%20the%20TMC%20dropped%20sitting%20MP%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20and%20fielded%20its%20former%20MP%20Haji%20Nurul%20Islam%20from%20Basirhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Names%20In%20The%20Fray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor-turned-politician%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Asansol%20seat%20byelection%20in%202022%20on%20a%20Trinamool%20ticket%2C%20has%20been%20re-nominated.%20Similarly%2C%20Kirti%20Azad%2C%20a%20former%20cricketer%20who%20joined%20the%20Trinamool%20in%202021%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20from%20the%20Bardhaman-Durgapur%20constituency.%20The%20seat%20was%20won%20by%20S.S.%20Ahluwalia%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20notable%20fresh%20faces%20fielded%20is%20also%20Debangshu%20Bhattacharya%2C%20the%20TMC's%20spokesperson%20and%20youth%20leader%20who%20devised%20the%20slogan%20'Khela%20Hobe'%20slogan%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20polls.%20Mamata's%20nephew%20and%20heir%20apparent%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20been%20renominated%20from%20Diamond%20Harbour%2C%20and%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20BJP's%20bete%20noire%2C%20has%20been%20rewarded%20with%20a%20ticket%20from%20Krishnanagar%20despite%20being%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20year%20in%20a%20cash-for-query%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20Of%20Peripheral%20Parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20front%2C%20though%20a%20weak%20player%20in%20Bengal%20today%2C%20had%20been%20wary%20of%20a%20possible%20Congress-TMC%20alliance%20as%20it%20would%20have%20been%20detrimental%20to%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20former%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20the%20Left%20Front%20is%20not%20averse%20to%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20TMC%20at%20a%20national%20level%2C%20it%20is%20careful%20not%20to%20ruin%20its%20limited%20chances%20in%20the%20old%20stronghold%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20Conversely%2C%20even%20the%20TMC%20was%20cautious%20about%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Left%20as%20there%20was%20apprehension%20that%20the%20anti-Mamata%20vote%20in%20the%20Left%20bloc%20would%20then%20shift%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Secular%20Front%20(ISF)%2C%20formed%20in%202021%2C%20and%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20its%20sole%20MLA%2C%20Naushad%20Siddiqui%2C%20is%20another%20worry%20for%20the%20Left%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20TMC.%20Both%20parties%20are%20anxious%20about%20Siddiqui's%20whirlwind%20tour%20of%20the%20state%20as%20it%20can%20mar%20their%20chances%20in%20several%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20wanted%20to%20break%20the%20Congress-ISF-Left%20alliance%20as%20it%20would've%20weaned%20away%20Muslim%20votes%20of%20the%20TMC.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20an%20increased%20vote%20percentage%2C%20would%20have%20managed%20to%20win%20more%20seats.%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20played%20spoilsport%20and%20TMC%20decided%20to%20go%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Diptendra%20Raychaudhuri%2C%20a%20Kolkata-based%20political%20analyst%2C%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20ISF%20and%20its%20impact.%20%26quot%3BBut%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20impact%20of%20Naushad%20Siddiqui's%20charisma%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20worry%20for%20TMC.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Khela%20Hobe'%202.0%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20doesn't%20like%20playing%20second%20fiddle.%20Having%20been%20safely%20ensconced%20in%20her%20chief%20ministerial%20chair%2C%20she%20is%20doing%20her%20best%20to%20be%20the%20sole%20challenger%20to%20the%20BJP%20nationally.%20She%20loves%20scoring%20a%20smart%2C%20subtle%20but%20hard-hitting%20win.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20elections%2C%20she%20appeared%20in%20front%20of%20the%20public%20with%20a%20cast%20in%20her%20leg.%20She%20eventually%20won-and%20celebrated%20the%20win%20with%20the%20cast%20nowhere%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Khela%20Hobe'%202.0%20is%20certainly%20on%20the%20anvil.%20The%20TMC%20secured%2043.3%25%20votes%20against%20the%20BJP's%2040.7%25%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Will%20Sandeshkhali%20change%20things%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqm3qh9ng_mamata-banerjee_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamatas-solo-act-in-west-bengal-is-a-big-setback-for-india-5225002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20TMC's%20decision%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20visible%20friction%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20extended%20from%20confrontations%20over%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20seat-sharing%20talks%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury's%20persistent%20personal%20attacks%20against%20Mamata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamatas-solo-act-in-west-bengal-is-a-big-setback-for-india-5225002%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamatas-solo-act-in-west-bengal-is-a-big-setback-for-india-5225002%2Famp%2