0Minister%20Om%20Prakash%20Chautala.%20While%20Abhay%20Chautala%20remained%20with%20the%20parent%20party%2C%20Dushyant%20and%20Digvijay%2C%20sons%20of%20his%20elder%20brother%20Abhay%20Singh%20Chautala%2C%20founded%20the%20JJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20its%20formation%2C%20the%20JJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20performance%20in%20the%202019%20Haryana%20elections%2C%20winning%2010%20seats.%20The%20party%20ate%20into%20the%20support%20base%20of%20its%20parent%20party%20INLD%2C%20which%20was%20reduced%20to%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20JJP%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20government%20in%20Haryana.%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20got%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20and%20JJP%20three%20cabinet%20berths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20months%20now%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20about%20the%20BJP%20and%20JJP%20parting%20ways.%20The%20Dushyant%20Chautala-led%20party%20had%20reportedly%20asked%20for%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20but%20BJP%20was%20offering%20only%20one.%20When%20no%20breakthrough%20could%20be%20reached%2C%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20the%20plug.%20The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20stepped%20down%20and%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%2040%20members%20in%20the%2090-seat%20Assembly%20and%20it%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%20some%20Independents%20and%20a%20breakaway%20group%20of%20JJP%20MLAs%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20comfortable%20majority.%20Interestingly%2C%20five%20JJP%20MLAs%20skipped%20a%20meeting%20at%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20Delhi%20residence%20today%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20may%20have%20changed%20sides.%20JJP%20is%20likely%20to%20issue%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20its%20next%20move%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbdpaojb_dushyant-chautala_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhay-singh-chautala-dushyant-chautala-haryana-uncles-betrayal-dig-at-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5224869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20BJP%20revamped%20its%20government%20in%20Haryana%20and%20potentially%20effected%20a%20split%20within%20the%20Dushyant%20Chautala-led%20Jananyak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP)%2C%20his%20uncle%20and%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20leader%20Abhay%20Singh%20Chautala%20took%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20the%20nephew%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhay-singh-chautala-dushyant-chautala-haryana-uncles-betrayal-dig-at-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5224869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhay-singh-chautala-dushyant-chautala-haryana-uncles-betrayal-dig-at-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5224869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhay-singh-chautala-dushyant-chautala-haryana-uncles-betrayal-dig-at-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5224869%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%3A%20With%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20CM%2C%20BJP%20Banks%20on%20Non-Jat%20Votes%20to%20Retain%20Power%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12172628%2Fimage-1943-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20By%20choosing%20its%20state%20unit%20chief%20and%20Kurukshetra%20MP%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20the%20new%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20once%20again%20has%20banked%20on%20the%20consolidation%20of%20non-Jats%20to%20win%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20assembly%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaini%20belongs%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20community%2C%20which%20makes%20up%20the%20largest%20share%20(40%25)%20of%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayab%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Saini%20caste%20alone%20makes%20up%208%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Saini%20driving%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20caste-centric%20politics%20of%20Haryana%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20party%20is%20focusing%20majorly%20on%20OBCs%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%20to%20counter%20anti-incumbency%20from%20its%20previous%20government%20under%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sign%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20consolidation%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20it%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20Jats-backed%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20in%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Saini%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20formed%20with%20support%20from%20independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20JJP%20MLAs%20may%20also%20defect%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJP%20stayed%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20under%20Khattar%20for%20four-and-a-half%20years%20before%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20move%2C%20though%20surprising%2C%20had%20been%20building%20up%20for%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20not%20confident%20in%20replicating%20its%20electoral%20performance%20in%202019%2C%20when%20it%20secured%20ten%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20later%20retained%20power%20with%20the%20JJP%E2%80%99s%20support%20in%20the%20assembly.its%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20changing%20its%20chief%20minister%20to%20an%20OBC%20face%2C%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20it%20will%20overcome%20the%20previous%20government%E2%80%99s%20challenges%2C%20especially%20when%20such%20an%20experiment%20has%20worked%20for%20it%20in%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20Khattar%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20social%20engineering%2C%20but%20his%20growing%20unpopularity%20made%20it%20tough%20for%20the%20party%20to%20match%20its%20previous%20poll%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoll%20experts%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Saini%20formula%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20non-Jats%20continue%20to%20support%20the%20party%20and%20that%20the%20leadership%20change%20is%20actually%20an%20excuse%20for%20course%20correction%20and%20intended%20to%20hide%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20past%20follies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20believe%20this%20may%20benefit%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20is%20leveraging%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20Modi%20brand%20to%20sway%20voters%2C%20but%20that%20such%20gains%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20later%20are%20not%20yet%20a%20done%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20caste%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20caste-centric%20politics%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Jats%2C%20comprising%20around%2025%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20have%20traditionally%20played%20a%20dominant%20role%20for%20decades%2C%20as%20other%20non-Jat%20communities%20either%20remained%20divided%20or%20aligned%20with%20the%20Jats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20social%20engineering%20during%20the%20Modi%20era%20has%20altered%20the%20electoral%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20seen%20only%20as%20a%20party%20of%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20voters%20and%20urban%20voters%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20changed%20under%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20after%20the%20party%20got%20a%20chunk%20of%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20votes%20in%20addition%20to%20support%20from%20the%20Brahmins%2C%20Punjabi%20and%20Baniya%20communities%20both%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20assembly%20polls%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Vijay%20Chauhan%2C%20assistant%20professor%20at%20department%20of%20political%20science%20in%20the%20Maharana%20Pratap%20National%20College%2C%20Mullana%20(Ambala)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Saini%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20politics%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20reward%20it%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20by%20elevating%20Saini%2C%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20repeats%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20when%20it%20won%20all%20ten%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20government%20formation%2C%20Chauhan%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20strategy%20to%20divide%20the%20Jat%20vote%20bank%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jat%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20state%20is%20largely%20divided%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20and%20its%20splinter%20group%2C%20the%20JJP.%20By%20dumping%20the%20JJP%20and%20letting%20it%20fight%20alone%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20clearly%20trying%20to%20split%20Jat%20votes%20to%20its%20favour%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20all%20Jat%20parties%20come%20on%20a%20common%20platform%20to%20stay%20in%2C%20fight%20or%20play%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20terms%2C%20said%20Chauhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20a%20Gujarat-like%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20eyes%20electoral%20benefits%20beyond%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20BJP%20changed%20the%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20months%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20In%20Haryana%20too%2C%20it%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20retains%20power%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20that%20are%20slated%20to%20take%20place%20soon%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20are%20already%20claiming%20a%20clean%20sweep.%20Karnal%20BJP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Bhatia%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20party%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20all%20ten%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20as%20well%20as%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20JJP%20state%20president%20Nishan%20Singh%20informed%20the%20media%20that%20a%20decision%20regarding%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20announced%20tomorrow%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Hisar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESaini%20takes%20oath%20with%20independents%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20support%20from%20independent%20candidates%2C%20Saini%20took%20oath%20as%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%2011th%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20currently%20has%2041%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20state%20assembly%2C%20needed%20the%20support%20of%20five%20more%20MLAs%20to%20retain%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20five%20of%20six%20independent%20MLAs%20have%20already%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Sirsa%20MLA%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%2C%20Gopal%20Kanda%2C%20also%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%20for%20their%20loyalty%2C%20one%20independent%20MLA%2C%20Ranjit%20Singh%20took%20oath%20as%20minister%20along%20with%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20Banwari%20Lal%2C%20Jai%20Parkash%20Dalal%2C%20Kanwar%20Pal%20Gujjar%20and%20Moolchand%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20accepted%20the%20moral%20defeat%20and%20Khattar%E2%80%99s%20failure%3A%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20said%20that%20by%20changing%20its%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accepted%20its%20moral%20defeat%20besides%20the%20failure%20of%20its%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20breaking%20of%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP%20was%20not%20surprising.%20There%20was%20an%20agreement%20between%20these%20two%20%5BBJP%20and%20JJP%5D%20to%20break%20the%20alliance%20because%20this%20alliance%20has%20totally%20failed.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20policy-based%20alliance%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98thugbandhan%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20people%20have%20realised%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710245716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12172628%2Fimage-1943-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-with-nayab-singh-saini-as-cm-bjp-banks-on-non-jat-votes-to-retain-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20sign%20of%20the%20party's%20non-Jat%20consolidation%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20it%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20Jats-backed%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20in%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Saini%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20formed%20with%20independents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-with-nayab-singh-saini-as-cm-bjp-banks-on-non-jat-votes-to-retain-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-driver%20sues%20F1%2C%20Bernie%20Ecclestone%20and%20FIA%20over%20world%20champion%20claims%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%20%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%20%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710245340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-felipa-massa-f1-crashgate_6487939.jpg%3F20240312122951%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fex-ferrari-driver-sues-formula-one-bernie-ecclestone-and-fia-over-2008-world-champion-claims160-13093173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Felipe%20