%20of%20the%20Act.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAASU%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20anti-foreigner%20agitation%20since%20the%201980s%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20Assam%20Accord%2C%20announced%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebandh%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAASU%20chief%20advisor%20Samujjal%20Bhattacharya%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Fbiggest-blow-to-assamese-people-anti-caa-agitators-issue-protest-call-2931771%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAA%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20us.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20today%20delivered%20the%20biggest%20blow%20to%20the%20Assamese%20people%2C%20our%20identity%2C%20and%20our%20culture.%20Our%20protest%20will%20continue.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAA%20nullifies%20the%20citizenship%20cut-off%20date%20of%20March%201971%20as%20per%20the%20Accord.%20As%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20Hindu%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20state%20till%202019%20is%20eligible%20for%20citizenship%20and%20can%20settle%20permanently%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20political%20parties%20which%20were%20born%20of%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20legislation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Raijor%20Dal%20and%20the%20Asam%20Jatiya%20Parishad%20(AJP)%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20announced%20a%20%E2%80%98hartal%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Fbiggest-blow-to-assamese-people-anti-caa-agitators-issue-protest-call-2931771%5C%22%3Eurged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Assamese%20people%20to%20come%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20to%20register%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAJP%20president%20Lurinjyoti%20Gogoi%20called%20March%2011%20%E2%80%9Ca%20black%20day%20for%20Assam%E2%80%9D%20and%20condemned%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20governments%20both%20at%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre%20for%20not%20heeding%20the%20Assamese%20people%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20to%20implementation%20of%20the%20the%20Act%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Act%20will%20crush%20the%20identity%2C%20land%20and%20cultural%20rights%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(previously%20called%20Twitter).%20Accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20seeking%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Assamese%20community%20to%20protect%20their%20rights%20but%20ending%20up%20giving%20it%20the%20biggest%20blow%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20from%20Assam%20like%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%20and%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20failed%20to%20convince%20their%20central%20government%20to%20keep%20Assam%20out%20of%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20a%20black%20day%20for%20Assam%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20urge%20people%20to%20get%20ready%20to%20fight%20this%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmore-than-four-years-after-caa-was-passed-union-government-to-notify-rules%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20Day%20SC%20Orders%20SBI%20to%20Reveal%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Data%2C%20Union%20Govt%20Announces%20Implementation%20of%20CAA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%2011%20night%2C%20Akhil%20Gogoi%2C%20MLA%20from%20the%20Sibsagar%20constituency%2C%20came%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20Golaghat%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20party%20workers%2C%20and%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%2012%20morning%2C%20he%20led%20a%20protest%20by%20his%20party%20at%20Sibsagar%20as%20part%20of%20a%20day-long%20joint%20%E2%80%9CSarbatmak%20Hartal%E2%80%9D%20called%20by%2016%20like-minded%20Opposition%20parties%20across%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20cooperating%20with%20us.%20I%20urge%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20draconian%20black%20law%20which%20will%20completely%20deprive%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Assam%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20said%20on%20X%20on%20March%2012%20afternoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20peaceful%20demonstration%20against%20C(A)A%20at%20Sivasagar%20today%2C%20a%20legal%20notice%20U%2FS%20152%20Cr.%20PC%2C%201973%20have%20been%20served%20to%20me%20while%20I%20was%20at%20the%20Circuit%20House%20by%20the%20government%2C%20thenceforth%2C%20ordering%20me%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9CUnited%20Opposition%20Forum%E2%80%9D%20to%20withdraw%20%E2%80%9CSarbatmak%20Hartal%E2%80%9D.%20Such%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbsccfMxqJL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbsccfMxqJL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20(%40AkhilGogoiAG)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAkhilGogoiAG%2Fstatus%2F1767465910561079393%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20the%20joint%20opposition%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20United%20Opposition%20Forum%20of%20Assam%20has%20written%20to%20the%20president%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20urging%20them%20to%20exclude%20Assam%20from%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20CAA.%20They%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20strong%20perception%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20irrespective%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20political%20affiliation%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%202019%20will%20put%20in%20danger%20the%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20socio-economic%20condition%2C%20social%20fabric%20and%20identity%20of%20Assamese%20people.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20forum%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20also%20said%20that%20if%20it%20is%20implemented%20in%20Assam%2C%20they%20would%20resort%20to%20a%20strike.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvolatile-situation-likely-to-arise-if-caa-implemented-16-assam-opposition-parties-to-modi%5C%22%3EUOFA%E2%80%99s%20letter%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20the%20prime%20minister%20warned%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvolatile%20situation%20(is)%20likely%20to%20arise%20in%20Assam%20in%20the%20coming%20days%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20demonstration%2C%20Gogoi%20was%20served%20a%20legal%20notice%20by%20the%20state%20police%2C%20asking%20his%20party%20and%20other%20like-minded%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20withdraw%20the%20protest%20call%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notice%20termed%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehartal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20and%20unconstitutional%E2%80%9D%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cvarious%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Kerala%20high%20court%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20regard%2C%20your%20attention%20is%20drawn%20to%20the%20specific%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20honourable%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20in%20writ%20petition%20%C2%A9%207570%2F2013%20dated%2019%20March%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%20The%20legal%20notice%20also%20threatened%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20there%20is%20any%20damage%20to%20public%2Fprivate%20property%20including%20railway%20and%20national%20highway%20properties%20or%20injury%C2%A0%20to%20any%20citizen%C2%A0%20caused%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98Sarbatmak%20Hartal%E2%80%99%2C%20legal%20action%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20initiated.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20notice%20is%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20threat%20some%20days%20ago%20to%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20Assam.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20order%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20that%20if%20political%20parties%20call%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebandh%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20protest%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20in%20Assam%2C%20he%20would%20write%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20deregister%20them.%20Sarma%20is%20also%20the%20state%20home%20minister.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20the%20legal%20notice%20served%20by%20the%20state%20police%2C%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20undemocratic%20and%20dictatorial%20steps%20of%20government%20sets%20a%20bad%20precedent%20against%20the%20upholding%20of%20democratic%20culture%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20MHA%20notifying%20the%20CAA%20before%20the%20general%20election%20dates%20are%20announced%2C%20the%20Sarma%20administration%2C%20since%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20have%20increased%20police%20presence%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Guwahati%20and%20several%20other%20cities%20and%20towns%20of%20the%20state.%20On%20March%2012%20morning%2C%20people%20noticed%20state%20police%20commandos%20marching%20on%20the%20city%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20to%20X%2C%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20G.P.%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAssam%20Police%20has%20made%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20breaks%20any%20law.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20protecting%20lives%20and%20property%20of%20residents%20of%20Assam%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20vandalism.%20Further%2C%20all%20laws%20and%20judicial%20pronouncements%20shall%20be%20fully%20implemented%20in%20accordance%20with%20laid%20down%20procedures.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202019%2C%20when%20the%20CAA%20was%20passed%20in%20Parliament%2C%20the%20state%20witnessed%20m