%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20excerpts%20from%20the%20essays%20in%20%3Cem%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20Places%3A%20An%20Architectural%20Documentation.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Built%20World%20of%20M.K.%20Gandhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Riyaz%20Tayyibji%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Satyagraha%20Ashram%20at%20Kocharab%20would%20be%20a%20short%20experiment%20as%20the%20handsome%20house%20in%20which%20it%20was%20based%20was%20on%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20that%20was%20insufficient%20for%20all%20the%20activities%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20in%20mind.%20In%20June%201917%20he%20would%20shift%20to%20a%20site%20measuring%20%E2%80%9855%20bighas%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20river%20Sabarmati%20near%20the%20central%20jail.%20Aghors%2C%20with%20their%20naked%20ash%20covered%20bodies%20would%20have%20been%20seen%20walking%20along%20the%20river%20to%20and%20past%20a%20nearby%20crematorium%20on%20the%20path%20that%20Gandhi%20would%20take%20when%20leaving%20the%20ashram%20for%20good%2C%20on%20his%20march%20to%20Dandi%20in%201930.%20In%201933%20he%20would%20dismantle%20the%20Ashram%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20an%20%3Ci%3EUdyog%20Mandir%3A%20A%20temple%20to%20Industry%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewhose%20programs%20would%20now%20revolve%20around%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20at%20the%20Ashram%20would%20start%20in%201917%2C%20but%20would%20proceed%20slowly%20due%20to%20the%20plague%2C%20the%20Ahmedabad%20mill%20workers%20strike%2C%20the%20Kheda%20Satyagraha%20and%20his%20own%20continuous%20travels%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20repeatedly%20visits%20Bombay%20and%20Delhi%2C%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%20while%20paying%20special%20attention%20to%20Madras%20and%20the%20south%2C%20only%20taking%20breaks%20for%20illness%20or%20when%20civil%20disobedience%20was%20suspended.%20So%20intense%20is%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20touring%20that%20by%20early%201920%20he%20is%20visiting%2020%20towns%20a%20month%20sometimes%20giving%20three%20speeches%20a%20day%20to%20an%20ever%20growing%20and%20reverent%20audience.%20When%20Gandhi%20did%20intermittently%20spend%20time%20at%20the%20ashram%20the%20school%20and%20weaving%20program%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20self-reliance%20would%20receive%20his%20most%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20absence%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20buildings%20at%20the%20Ashram%20were%20managed%20by%20Maganlal%20Gandhi.%20The%20school%20and%20the%20weaving%20shed%20were%20the%20first%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20hand.%20The%20latter%20would%20be%20used%20for%20living%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20other%20accommodation1.%20Soon%20communal%20farming%2C%20weaving%20and%20animal%20husbandry%20would%20also%20begin.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20his%20friend%20in%20South%20Africa%20A.H.%20West%2C%20Gandhi%20would%20write%2C%20%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ashram%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3Eis%20beautifully%20situated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Sabarmati%20river.%20We%20daily%20bathe%20in%20it.%20All%20the%20children%20can%20swim%20now.%20The%20school%20is%20under%20an%20able%20Principal%20who%20was%20a%20distinguished%20professor%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20College.%20The%20Ashram%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20under%20Maganlal%E2%80%99s%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12160856%2Fimage-1936.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12160856%2Fimage-1936.png%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12160856%2Fimage-1936-300x148.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12160856%2Fimage-1936-1024x505.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes