huk%2C%20who%20is%20on%20hunger%20strike%20to%20demand%20special%20status%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20Ladakhis%20now%20feel%20it%20%5BLadakh%5D%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20in%20the%20olden%20times%20and%20officers%20from%20faraway%20places%20come%20to%20govern%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%2C%20whose%20life%20inspired%20the%20character%20of%20Phunsukh%20Wangdu%2C%20played%20by%20Aamir%20Khan%20in%20Bollywood%20blockbuster%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20observing%20a%2021-day%20fast%2C%20amid%20freezing%20temperatures%2C%20to%20press%20for%20the%20Union%20Territory%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20under%20the%20sixth%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20statehood.%20These%20demands%20have%20dominated%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20region%20after%20Ladakh%20was%20dismembered%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20granted%20a%20Union%20Territory%20status%20in%202019%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20the%20fast%20on%20March%206%20after%20parleys%20between%20leadership%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20Union%20home%20ministry%20reached%20a%20dead-end%20with%20the%20Apex%20Body%20Leh%20(ABL)%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%20saying%20that%20the%20sub-committee%20level%20talks%20and%20their%20separate%20meeting%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20didn%E2%80%99t%20yield%20any%20concrete%20and%20positive%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20phone%20from%20the%20venue%20of%20his%20hunger%20strike%2C%20Wangchuk%2C%20who%20entered%20the%207th%20day%20of%20his%20strike%20today%2C%20said%20that%20Ladakhis%20are%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20dejected%2C%20disappointed%20and%20frustrated%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20careless%20and%20insensitive%E2%80%9D%20towards%20genuine%20demands%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20set-up%20a%20bad%20precedent%20of%20distrust%20for%20the%20entire%20nation%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%20You%20can%20make%20any%20promise%20and%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20Electoral%20promises%20and%20manifestos%20will%20have%20no%20meaning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20BJP%20regarding%20inclusion%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20sixth%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20once%2C%20they%20made%20the%20same%20promise%20twice.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20was%20among%20their%20top%20three%20promises%20and%20in%202020%20Hill%20Council%20polls%2C%20it%20was%20their%20topmost%20promise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sixth%20schedule%20provides%20for%20the%20administration%20of%20certain%20tribal%20areas%20as%20autonomous%20entities.%20It%20allows%20creation%20of%20autonomous%20district%20councils%20and%20regional%20councils%20endowed%20with%20certain%20legislative%2C%20executive%2C%20judicial%20and%20financial%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20videos%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Wangchuk%C2%A0has%20been%20seeking%20special%20status%20for%20the%20region%20to%20safeguard%20its%20fragile%20environs%20and%20glaciers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20that%20certain%20quarters%20are%20citing%20the%20small%20size%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20population%20to%20oppose%20its%20demand%20for%20statehood%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Sikkim%20became%20a%20state%2C%20it%20had%20roughly%202.50%20lakh%20population%20and%20Ladakh%20today%20has%20three%20lakh%20population.%20When%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20are%20right%2C%20they%20can%20do%20things%20and%20when%20it%20is%20not%2C%20they%20can%20get%20away%20with%20excuses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ladakhis%20now%20feel%20it%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20and%20commissioners%20from%20some%20faraway%20places%20come%20and%20govern%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20democracy%2C%20no%20voting%20rights%20to%20elect%20their%20representatives%20to%20an%20Assembly.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20in%20the%20olden%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%20said%20that%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20mobilise%20people%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20to%20express%20their%20opinion%2C%20maybe%20through%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20calmly%20elect%20the%20right%20people%20and%20reject%20the%20wrong%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20whether%20Ladakhis%20would%20express%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20these%20demands%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20is%20touched%20by%20the%20bonhomie%20between%20people%20of%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20over%20these%20serious%20issues%20which%20have%20far-reaching%20effects%20for%20a%20longtime%20to%20come.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20sad%20incident%20has%20some%20positive%20aspects.%20The%20people%20have%20united%20and%20resolved%20their%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20and%20Muslim-majority%20Kargil%20have%20been%20arch-rivals%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20they%20have%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20for%20sixth%20schedule%20and%20statehood%20for%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-seven-year-old%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20is%20an%20engineer%2C%20innovator%20and%20education%20reformist.%20He%20is%20the%20founding-director%20of%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Educational%20and%20Cultural%20Movement%20of%20Ladakh%20founded%20in%201988.%20Wangchuk%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20launch%20of%20operation%20New%20Hope%20in%201994%2C%20a%20collaboration%20of%20government%2C%20village%20communities%20and%20civil%20society%20to%20bring%20reforms%20in%20the%20government%20school%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%20his%20efforts%20to%20develop%20educational%20reform%20programmes%20that%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%9Ccreative%2C%20child-friendly%2C%20and%20activity-based%E2%80%9D%20education%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710242101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F28165517%2FScreenshot-2023-01-28-at-4.55.03-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fladhak-is-like-a-colony-governed-by-officers-from-far-off-places-sonam-wangchuk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wangchuk%2C%20whose%20life%20inspired%20the%20character%20of%20Phunsukh%20Wangdu%20played%20by%20Aamir%20Khan%20in%20Bollywood%20blockbuster%203%20Idiots%2C%20is%20on%20day%207%20of%20his%2021-day%20hunger%20strike%20to%20demand%20special%20status%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fladhak-is-like-a-colony-governed-by-officers-from-far-off-places-sonam-wangchuk%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2215%20people%20killed%20after%20Russian%20military%20cargo%20plane%20crashes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108435214%2Cimgsize-1602662.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F15-people-killed-after-russian-military-cargo-plane-crashes%2Farticleshow%2F108435182.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108435182.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F15-people-killed-after-russian-military-cargo-plane-crashes%2Farticleshow%2F108435182.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F15-people-killed-after-russian-military-cargo-plane-crashes%2Famp_articleshow%2F108435182.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F15-people-killed-after-russian-military-cargo-plane-crashes%2Famp_articleshow%2F108435182.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20Paradox%3A%20Hindutva%20Is%20Gaining%20Fast%20but%20Modi%20Is%20Stealing%20RSS%20Thunder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Fwomen-face-uphill-climb-mother-of%5C%22%3Epiece%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98party%20with%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20newly%20re-born%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20used%20to%20boast%20during%20the%20%E2%80%9880s%20and%20%E2%80%9890s.%20The%20tag%20line%2C%20coined%20by%20K.R.%20Malkani%2C%20was%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20apt.%20Those%20were%20the%20days%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20bodies%20met%20at%20regular%20interval%20while%20the%20ruling%20party%20Congress%20followed%20the%20high%20command%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20bodies%20held%20free%20and%20fair%20discussions%20within%20the%20ideological%20framework%20of%20the%20RSS.%20The%20National%20Executive%20(NE)%20had%20quarterly%20meetings%20held%20at%20different%20state%20capitals.%20At%20the%20National%20Council%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20a%20three-day%20jamboree%20open%20to%20media%20%E2%80%93%20the%20delegates%20loudly%20held%20forth%20on%20party%20policies%20and%20internal%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20then%20and%20now%20is%20now.%20Consider%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20National%20Council%20meeting.%20It%20was%20dominated%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20address%20on%20both%20days%20and%20one%20each%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20J.P.%20Nadda.%20The%2011-page%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fpolitically-correct%2Fswamy-impact-shifting-goalposts-7-takeaways-from-bjps-national-convention%2F1971311%2F%5C%22%3Epolitical%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20Modi%20as%20many%20as%2084%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20special%20trains%20carried%20party%20delegates%20who%20mingled%20with%20the%20large%20number%20of%20correspondents%20present.%20Top%20leaders%20like%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20accompanied%20the%20train%20and%20interacted%20with%20delegates%20and%20media%20persons%2C%20in%20groups%20and%20individually.%20We%20had%20a%20fairly%20good%20idea%20about%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20presidents%2C%20on%20their%20part%2C%20did%20not%20announce%20any%20decision%20without%20consulting%20the%20NE%20or%20the%20office-bearers%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20RSS.%20Nagpur%20in%20those%20days%20encouraged%20a%20system%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20internal%20debate%20among%20the%20Parivar%20outfits.%20The%20NE%20was%20a%20lively%20forum%20which%20discussed%20and%20worked%20for%20consensus%20on%20contentious%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20some%20thing%20unthinkable%20under%20the%20MoSha%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20discussions%20were%20inconclusive%20and%20the%20NE%20had%20to%20put%20off%20consideration%20to%20the%20next%20meeting.%20For%20wider%20debate%20on%20specially%20contentious%20issues%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98chintan%20baithaks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20called.%20Such%20a%20wider%20conclave%20was%20held%20at%20Sariska%20on%20Narasimha%20Rao%E2%80%99s%201991%20economic%20reform%20when%20the%20Advani%20group%20sharply%20differed%20with%20the%20Swadeshi%20Jagran%20Manch%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20had%20the%20support%20of%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Malkani%2C%20K.L.%20Sharma%2C%20Sunder%20Singh%20Bhandari%20and%20Jai%20Dubashi.%20The%20Sariska%20conclave%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Gandhinagar%20session%20of%20the%20NE%20where%20an%20economic%20policy%20document%20detailing%20the%20%E2%80%98Swadeshi%20alternative%E2%80%99%20or%20Gandhinagar%20declaration%20was%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganisational%20elections%20were%20fairly%20free.%20And%20at%20local%20levels%2C%20the%20pre-Modi%20BJP%20had%20its%20share%20of%20allegations%20of%20fake%20voters%20lists%2C%20protests%20and%20boycotts%20%E2%80%93%20indications%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20polls.%20Decisions%20under%20the%20central%20observers%20were%20mostly%20by%20consensus%20at%20tehsil%2C%20district%20and%20state%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20ministers%20were%20fixed%20after%20a%20system%20of%20tenuous%20consultations%20among%20the%20RSS%20leaders%2C%20BJP%20legislators%20and%20leaders%20of%20various%20contending%20state%20factions.%20Unlike%20today%2C%20the%20carried%20juicy%20stories%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20different%20aspirants%20for%20the%20BJP%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20all%20this%20is%20history.%20The%20BJP%20as%20a%20political%20movement%20with%20organic%20links%20with%20its%20support%20base%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20past.%20Narendra%20Modi%20likes%20to%20directly%20deal%20with%20voters.%20Anything%20coming%20in%20between%20the%20leader%20and%20the%20voter%20is%20considered%20a%20hurdle%20and%20should%20be%20removed.%20That%20is%20the%20new%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20army%20of%20middle-level%20workers%20who%20had%20acted%20as%20a%20link%20and%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20taking%20the%20message%20to%20the%20grassroots%20are%20another%20casualty.%20Under%20the%20Modi-centric%20public%20discourse%20and%20election%20campaign%2C%20they%20have%20little%20role.%20With%20technology%20and%20an%20army%20of%20experts%2C%20the%20whole%20line%20of%20command%20has%20undergone%20drastic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20local%20levels%2C%20the%20traditional%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20workers%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20%3Cem%3Epanna%20pramukhs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20booth%20in-charges%20and%20similar%20kind%20of%20gophers.%20All%20profitable%20positions%20have%20been%20cornered%20by%20the%20glib%20talking%20smart%20set.%20They%20invariably%20use%20their%20new%20status%20for%20the%20enhancement%20of%20their%20business%20career.%20With%20such%20elements%20grabbing%20the%20enormous%20party%20funds%2C%20devoted%20traditional%20workers%20are%20gradually%20fading%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20every%20good%20elected%20dictator%2C%20Modi%20has%20an%20aversion%20for%20leaders%20with%20their%20own%20support%20base.%20During%20the%20good%20old%20internal%20democracy%20days%2C%20such%20leaders%20were%20treated%20as%20a%20great%20asset%20to%20the%20BJP.%20But%20Modi%20considers%20them%20as%20irritants%20and%20potential%20challengers.%20Hence%20he%20has%20eliminated%20all%20senior%20chief%20ministers.%20Last%20among%20the%20sidelined%20are%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20Their%20place%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20faceless%20new%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20era%20also%20presents%20a%20curious%20paradox.%20While%20the%20Hindutva%20cause%20has%20floruised%20immensely%2C%20the%20RSS%20under%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20suffered%20considerable%20erosion.%20Modi%20increasingly%20overshadows%20Bhagwat%20and%20his%20RSS.%20Modi%20has%20taken%20the%20role%20of%20a%20chief%20priest%20and%20pujari%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20in%20Ayodhya%20or%20Abu%20Dhabi%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20been%20anointed%20as%20the%20Hindu%20Hriday%20Samrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindutva%20crowds%20increasingly%20look%20to%20Modi%20for%20inspiration%20and%20as%20their%20hero.%20The%20epicenter%20of%20Hindutva%20is%20gradually%20moving%20from%20Nagpur%20to%20the%20PMO%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Modi%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20chief%20spokesman%20of%20Hindutva.%20The%20RSS%20has%20never%20suffered%20such%20an%20erosion%20of%20authority%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20this%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20the%20present%20RSS%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20tunnel%20vision.%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20predecessors%20like%20Rajubhayya%20and%20K.S.%20Sudarshan%20had%20a%20wider%20world%20view%20beyond%20Hindutva%2C%20Ayodhya%20and%20narrow%20hate%20politics.%20They%20believed%20that%20Hindu%20nationalism%20could%20be%20built%20only%20by%20a%20BJP%20government%20on%20a%20nationalistic%20socio-economic%20foundation%2C%20i.e.%20a%20Swadeshi%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20never%20allowed%20the%20emergence%20of%20authoritarian%20or%20all-powerful%20super%20bosses%20under%20their%20aegis.%20Instead%2C%20they%20insisted%20on%20consensus%20decisions%20and%20collective%20leadership.%20Consider%20the%20travails%20of%20BJP%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20whenever%20he%20tried%20to%20cross%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Lakshman%20Rekha.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20line%20or%20limit%20Modi%20can%E2%80%99t%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EP.%20Raman%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241755000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rss-paradox-hindutva-is-gaining-fast-but-modi-is-stealing-rss-thunder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20never%20allowed%20the%20emergence%20of%20authoritarian%20super%20bosses%20under%20their%20aegis.%20Instead%2C%20they%20insisted%20on%20consensus%20decisions%20and%20collective%20leadership.%20Consider%20the%20travails%20of%20BJP%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20whenever%20he%20tried%20to%20cross%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Lakshman%20Rekha.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20line%20or%20limit%20Modi%20can%E2%80%99t%20cross.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rss-paradox-hindutva-is-gaining-fast-but-modi-is-stealing-rss-thunder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20Is%20an%20Assault%20on%20Muslims%2C%20but%20It%20Will%20Come%20for%20Hindus%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12155110%2F640px-No_to_police_brutality_no_caa_no_nrc_graffiti_on_metro_wall_shaheen_bagh_protests_8_jan_2020.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20came%20as%20no%20surprise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%20They%20had%20been%20warned%20by%20their%20chief%20minister%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20that%20the%20registration%20of%20political%20parties%20that%20dared%20to%20protest%20against%20CAA%20would%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%20too%2C%20activists%20living%20in%20predominantly%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20neighbourhoods%E2%80%99%20witnessed%20an%20unusually%20heavy%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces.%20Some%20of%20the%20activists%20were%20also%20contacted%20by%20the%20police%20and%20warned%20politely%20not%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20any%20agitational%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20interesting%20instead%20is%20the%20timing%20if%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20right%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(SBI)%20plea%20to%20defer%20the%20date%20of%20revealing%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20It%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20reversal%20and%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20To%20prevent%20that%20from%20dominating%20the%20news%20space%2C%20another%20big%20news%20had%20to%20be%20manufactured.%20And%20what%20could%20be%20better%20than%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20are%20yet%20another%20iteration%20of%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20It%20can%20be%20summarised%20in%20one%20sentence%3A%20to%20tell%20Muslims%20that%20they%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20India%20in%20the%20same%20measure%20or%20manner%20in%20which%20Hindus%20do.%20The%20state%20will%20find%20ways%20to%20accommodate%20Hindus%20and%20exclude%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20lawyer%20Aman%20Wadud%20has%20been%20saying%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20help%20even%20the%20Hindus%20in%20Assam%2C%20who%20have%20been%20suffering%20after%20their%20exclusion%20from%20the%20NRC.%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%20they%20can%20not%20show%20the%20documents%20stipulated%20as%20essential%20to%20prove%20their%20belonging%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20claims%20to%20be%20an%20instrument%20that%20will%20help%20people%20of%20all%20religions%2C%20barring%20Muslims%2C%20who%20have%20suffered%20persecution%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20But%20it%20brings%20no%20relief%20to%20those%20Hindus%20who%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20are%20citizens%20of%20India%20but%20cannot%20show%20the%20papers%20asked%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20prove%20their%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20and%20its%20leaders%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20all%20Hindus%20would%20be%20included%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20act.%20But%20how%3F%20The%20CAA%20asks%20them%20to%20show%20that%20they%20were%20citizens%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20or%20Afghanistan.%20How%20will%20they%20do%20it%3F%20These%20Hindu%20citizens%2C%20numbering%20approximately%2015%20lakhs%2C%20would%20be%20left%20stateless.%20We%20must%20understand%20this%20before%20going%20into%20the%20real%20intent%20of%20the%20CAA%20and%20how%20it%20affects%20the%20secular%20character%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%2C%20the%20grounds%20of%20Indian%20citizenship%20have%20officially%20opened%20a%20path%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cfaith-based%E2%80%9D%20citizenship%20%E2%80%93%20a%20path%20open%20to%20everyone%20but%20Muslims.%20The%20real%20intent%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20CAA%20cannot%20be%20understood%20if%20we%20do%20not%20read%20it%20along%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20After%20all%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20been%20very%20clear%20about%20one%20gaining%20meaning%20in%20the%20company%20of%20the%20other.%20NRC%20is%20a%20process%20of%20exclusion%20and%20CAA%2C%20one%20of%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20have%20said%20time%20and%20again%20that%20NRC%20would%20weed%20out%20outsiders%20while%20CAA%20would%20include%20the%20left%20out%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined%20that%20NRC%20brings%20a%20very%20significant%20change%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%20With%20the%20NRC%2C%20we%20already%20saw%20a%20shift%20from%3Cem%3E%20jus%20soli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(citizenship%20by%20birth)%20to%20%3Cem%3Ejus%20sanguinis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(citizenship%20by%20descent).%20However%2C%20the%20affinity%20of%20CAA%20with%20NRC%20is%20not%20only%20fundamental%20but%20critical%20to%20its%20implementation%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20CAA-NRC%20really%20excluding%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20was%20made%20the%20perfect%20laboratory%20to%20execute%20this%20model%20of%20citizenship%20re-verification%20through%20NRC.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20state%20provided%20organic%20grounds%20to%20implement%20something%20like%20this%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20demands%20of%20the%20Assamese%20nationalists.%20The%20use%20of%20NRC%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%98foreigners%E2%80%99%20in%20Assam%20meant%20anyone%20who%20had%20ancestry%20in%20erstwhile%20East%20Bengal%2C%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20Their%20religion%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20to%20the%20Assamese%20nationalist%20whose%20long-standing%20demand%20was%20to%20identify%20those%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20Bengali%E2%80%9D%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENRC%20left%20out%20over%2019%20lakh%20people%20from%20the%20citizenship%20register.%20According%20to%20a%20Sabrang%20report%2C%20sourced%20to%20the%20Intelligence%20Brunch%20of%20Assam%2C%20only%20about%204.89%20lakh%20of%20the%20total%20belonged%20to%20Bengali%20origin%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20of%20the%20breakup%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20Bengali%20Hindus%20(6.90%20lakhs)%2C%20Gorkha%20(85%2C000)%2C%20Assamese%20Hindu%20(60%2C000)%2C%20Koch%20Rajbonshi%20(58%2C000)%2C%20Goria%20Moria%20Deshi%20(35%2C000)%2C%20Bodo%20(20%2C000)%2C%20Karbi%20(9%2C000)%2C%20Rabha%20(8%2C000)%2C%20Hajong%20(8%2C000)%2C%20Mishing%20(7%2C000)%2C%20Ahom%20(3%2C000)%2C%20Garo%20(2%2C500)%2C%20Matak%20(1%2C500)%2C%20Dimasa%20(1%2C100)%2C%20Sonowal%20Kachari%20(1%2C000)%2C%20Maran%20(900)%2C%20Bishnupriya%20Manipuri%20(200)%2C%20Naga%20(125)%2C%20Hmar%20(75)%2C%20Kuki%20(85)%2C%20Thadou%20(50)%2C%20Baite%20(85).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20can%20see%2C%20only%20a%20few%20of%20these%20people%20qualify%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20under%20CAA.%20Technically%2C%20the%20category%20of%20Original%20Inhabitants%20(OI)%20also%20takes%20away%20the%20doubt%20of%20many%20communities%20listed%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%2C%20the%20only%20community%20left%20out%20are%20the%20Bengali%20origin%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Assam.%20This%20makes%20them%20the%20primary%20political%20victims%20of%20the%20citizenship%20process%20of%20NRC.%20One%20can%20safely%20conclude%20that%20both%20the%20process%20are%20anti-Muslim%20projects%20of%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Saviour%20complex%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20tone%20of%20saviour%20complex.%20It%20is%20trying%20to%20claim%20that%20India%2C%20through%20CAA%2C%20is%20going%20to%20save%20the%20non-Muslim%20persecuted%20minorities%20in%20its%20neighbouring%20countries.%20Such%20is%20the%20control%20of%20the%20narrative%20in%20India.%20But%20we%20need%20to%20ask%20again%2C%20what%20about%20those%20poor%20Hindus%20who%20could%20not%20show%20the%20papers%3F%20The%20CAA%20don%E2%80%99t%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20say%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20that%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20announcement%20was%20never%20to%20help%20any%20community%20but%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20in%20which%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20are%20placed%20on%20unequal%20planes.%20As%20Sushil%20Aaron%20wrote%20way%20back%20in%202019%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20which%20process%20is%20applied%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20NRC%20process%20has%20been%20conceived%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20spares%20Hindus%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20the%20trouble%20of%20proving%20they%20are%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20since%20the%20CAA%20eventually%20offers%20pathways%20to%20Indian%20citizenship%20for%20them%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20does%20not%20provide%20to%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20is%20a%20psychological%20assault%20on%20Muslims%20by%20reinforcing%20anxieties%20about%20their%20existence%20as%20equal%20citizens.%20One%20CAA%20is%20here%2C%20can%20NRC%20be%20far%20behind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20of%20CAA%20also%20comes%20during%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%20The%20timing%20of%20this%20declaration%20is%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%20that%20is%20pregnant%20with%20violence%20against%20a%20community.%20This%20violence%20is%2C%20above%20all%20symbolic%2C%20in%20nature.%20In%20a%20month%20when%20peace%2C%20generosity%20and%20justice%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20is%20celebrated%20as%20virtues%2C%20this%20declaration%20is%20a%20stab%20at%20the%20very%20secularity%20of%20citizenship%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuraj%20Gogoi%20writes%20about%20citizenship%2C%20minority%2C%20nationalism%2C%20state%2C%20food%20and%20violence%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12155110%2F640px-No_to_police_brutality_no_caa_no_nrc_graffiti_on_metro_wall_shaheen_bagh_protests_8_jan_2020.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-is-an-assault-on-muslims-but-it-will-come-for-hindus-too%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20act%2C%20while%20eviscerating%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20the%20country%2C%20also%20offers%20no%20relief%20to%20those%20Hindus%20who%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20are%20citizens%20of%20India%20but%20cannot%20show%20the%20papers%20asked%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20prove%20their%20claim.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-is-an-assault-on-muslims-but-it-will-come-for-hindus-too%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fighting%20ongoing%20in%20Russian%20border%20regions%3A%20pro-Kyiv%20group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publis