m%20Festival%20held%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%2C%20a%20packed%20auditorium%20awarded%20a%20standing%20ovation%20to%20a%20documentary%20film%20by%20Nausheen%20Khan%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fshaheen-bagh-documentary-nausheen-khan%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELand%20of%20My%20Dreams.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20film%20documents%20the%20CAA-NRC-NPR%20protests%2C%20the%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20and%20the%20stories%20of%20resistance%20that%20emerged%20from%20them.%20The%20event%20ended%20with%20the%20host%20reminding%20the%20audience%20that%20even%20those%20present%20in%20the%20room%20were%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20event%2C%20residents%20of%20Shiv%20Vihar%2C%20Mustafabad%2C%20Jaffrabad%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20narrated%20with%20great%20strength%20and%20kindness%20the%20impact%20that%20resistance%20had%20on%20them%20%E2%80%93%20how%20important%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20midnight%20order%20was%20in%20reducing%20violence%20in%20the%20Hindutva-led%20riots%2C%20what%20it%20meant%20that%20we%20were%20gathered%20there%20to%20understand%20the%20growth%20of%20hate%20crime%20in%20India%2C%20and%20how%20the%20efforts%20of%20lawyers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20poets%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20activists%20were%20essential%20in%20continuing%20to%20care%20for%20justice.%20I%20felt%20hope%20despite%20the%20worries%20that%20any%20amount%20of%20visibility%2C%20even%20in%20the%20most%20tender%20efforts%20to%20provide%20care%20for%20those%20who%20had%20lost%20loved%20ones%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20would%20mean%20a%20possibility%20of%20state-enabled%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20event%2C%20residents%20of%20Shiv%20Vihar%2C%20Mustafabad%2C%20Jaffrabad%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20shared%20their%20stories%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20resistance.%20They%20spoke%20about%20the%20significance%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fdont-know-why-delhi-riots-order-upset-the-government-it-was-the-right-thing-to-do-justice-muralidhar-239588%5C%22%3E%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20midnight%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20quelling%20violence%20during%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20saw%20discussions%20on%20the%20rise%20of%20hate%20crimes%20in%20India%20and%20highlighted%20the%20indispensable%20role%20of%20lawyers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20poets%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20activists%20in%20pursuing%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20concerns%20about%20potential%20state-enabled%20persecution%2C%20there%20was%20a%20palpable%20sense%20of%20hope%20fueled%20by%20the%20collective%20efforts%20to%20provide%20care%20and%20support%20to%20those%20who%20had%20lost%20loved%20ones%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-implements-citizenship-amendment-act-check-the-caa-rules-here-92081%5C%22%3Ethe%20Centre%20notified%20the%20Rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CAA)%20after%20four%20years%20of%20continuously%20filing%20extensions.%20The%20move%20came%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-sbi-just-has-to-open-sealed-cover-give-details-sc-raps-bank-101710136137207.html%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20rapped%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20lack%20of%20compliance%20with%20releasing%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20arrived%2C%20chatter%20began%20on%20the%20move%E2%80%99s%20form%2C%20intent%2C%20and%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20overwhelmed%20me%2C%20of%20what%20this%20meant%20and%20what%20now%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20ministers%20of%20the%20governments%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3