g%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20right-wing%20groups%20to%20further%20%E2%80%9Cbully%20Indian%20Muslims%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaduddin%20Owaisi%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasadowaisi%2Fstatus%2F1767182248246178025%5C%22%3Econnected%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20announcement%20of%20the%20Rules%20as%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20election%20period%20and%20criticised%20the%20CAA%20for%20its%20divisive%20nature%2C%20as%20based%20on%20Nathuram%20Godse%E2%80%99s%20logic%20of%20reducing%20Muslims%20to%20second-class%20citizens.%20He%20ended%20his%20tweet%20with%20a%20note%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndians%20who%20came%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20to%20oppose%20CAA%2C%20NPR%2C%20NRC%20will%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20oppose%20it%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Amnesty%20India%20said%20that%20the%20CAA%20goes%20against%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20constitutional%20values%20of%20equality%20and%20human%20rights%20law%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20multiple%20international%20covenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20these%20events%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheQuint%2Fstatus%2F1767218869112918477%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%20breaking%20out%20against%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Rules%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20across%20multiple%20districts%20in%20Assam.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcaa-rules-live-updates-9208276%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20student%20unions%20burn%20copies%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20declaring%20a%20statewide%20%E2%80%98hartal%E2%80%99%20on%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fanti-caa-bandh-assam-cm-reminds-political-parties-of-high-court-restriction%2Farticle67935750.ece%5C%22%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20said%20that%20political%20parties%20faced%20the%20risk%20of%20deregistration%20if%20they%20organised%20anti-CAA%20protests%2C%20citing%20the%202023%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20order%20that%20declared%20bandhs%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20and%20unconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMaktoob%20Media%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20shared%20footage%20of%20protests%20that%20quickly%20erupted%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC4YiWq7szvW%2F%5C%22%3EKozhikode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20students%20were%20subjected%20to%20violent%20lathi%20charges.%20Additionally%2C%20late-night%20vigils%20were%20held%20by%20student%20organisations%20including%20Fraternity%2C%20MSF%2C%20and%20NSU(I)%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC4Yas1CvjX3%2F%5C%22%3EJamia%20Millia%20Islamia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC4Za9k2i8UD%2F%5C%22%3EHyderabad%20Central%20University%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Rules%20seems%20obviously%20oriented%20towards%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20communal%20division%20as%20a%20mode%20of%20increased%20voter%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fbjp-gains-in-polls-after-every-riot-says-yale-study%2Farticleshow%2F45378840.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EYale%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20grew%20by%200.08%25%20after%20each%20incident%20of%20communal%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20Rules%20themselves%20reveal%20that%20applications%20for%20the%20CAA%20are%20to%20be%20made%20via%20an%20online%20portal%20(indiancitizenshiponline.nic.in)%2C%20where%20applicants%20would%20be%20then%20issued%20with%20a%20digital%20certificate%20of%20registration%20or%20a%20digital%20certificate%20of%20naturalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rules%20further%20confirm%20that%20only%20persons%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20who%20belong%20to%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%2C%20or%20Christian%20identities%20would%20be%20considered%20for%20citizenship%20under%20the%20Act.%20A%20person%20making%20an%20application%20through%20the%20CAA%20for%20citizenship%20would%20thus%20need%20to%20provide%20a%C2%A0%20minimum%20of%20five%20to%20six%20documents.%20These%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ei)%3Cstrong%3E%20a%20filled%20application%20form%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eii)%3Cstrong%3E%20one%20of%20the%20documents%20listed%20under%20Schedule%20IA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20land%20or%20tenancy%20records%20from%20the%20origin%20country%2C%20birth%20certificates%2C%20identity%20documents%2C%20land%20or%20tenancy%20records%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eiii)%3Cstrong%3E%20one%20of%20the%20documents%20from%20Schedule%20IB%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esuch%20as%20ration%20card%2C%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20license%2C%20any%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20Government%20or%20Court%20to%20the%20applicant%20with%20an%20official%20stamp%2C%20land%20or%20tenancy%20records%2C%20electricity%20papers%2C%20school%20leaving%20certificates%2C%20and%20others%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eiv)%20%3Cstrong%3Ean%20affidavit%20verifying%20the%20correctness%20of%20statements%20made%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20as%20attested%20by%20a%20Notary%2FOath%20Commissioner%2FMagistrate%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ev)%20a%20document%20providing%20evidence%20that%20an%20applicant%20or%20either%20of%20their%20parents%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20Independent%20India%20(passport%20or%20birth%20certificate)%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Evi)%20if%20available%2C%20the%20copy%20of%20an%20expired%20Foreign%20Passport%20or%20Residential%20Permit%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20completed%20application%20would%20then%20be%20processed%20by%20a%20District%20Level%20Committee%2C%20and%20then%20if%20verified%2C%20the%20designated%20officer%20would%20administer%20an%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20applicant%20in%20person%2C%20then%20sent%20to%20the%20Empowered%20Committee.%20The%20final%20digital%20certificate%20would%20be%20issued%20with%20the%20signature%20of%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Empowered%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20portal%20further%20includes%20guidelines%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiancitizenshiponline.nic.in%2FDocuments%2FUserGuide%2Fordersection6B_rule_11A.pdf%5C%22%3Ecomposition%20of%20the%20two%20committees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Empowered%20Committee%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20Director%20of%20Census%20Operations%2C%20is%20to%20be%20formed%20by%20an%20intelligence%20bureau%20officer%2C%20a%20Foreigners%20Regional%20Registration%20Officer%2C%20a%20State%20Informatics%20Officer%2C%20a%20Postal%20Officer%20or%20Post%20Master%20General%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Railways%20and%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Principal%20or%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary.%20The%20District%20Level%20Committee%20would%20compromise%20a%20District%20Informatics%20Officer%2C%C2%A0%20representative%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20Naib%20Tehsildar%2C%20a%20nominee%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20and%20a%20jurisdictional%20Station%20Master%20of%20Railways.%20The%20required%20quorum%20for%20each%20of%20the%20Committees%20is%20only%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20leaves%20room%20for%20corruption%20and%20mistreatment%20of%20applicants%20both%20at%20the%20District%20Level%20Committee%20and%20with%20the%20Empowered%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20composition%2C%20which%20includes%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20officers%20and%20vaguely%20described%20nominees%20of%20the%20central%20government%2C%20with%20their%20meagre%20quorum%20of%20two%20individuals%2C%20creates%20an%20uncertain%20and%20unfair%20system%20of%20authentication%20and%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20limited%20measures%20to%20check%20any%20oversight%20by%20members%20of%20the%20District%20Level%20and%20Empowered%20Committees%20and%20to%20prevent%20the%20abuse%20of%20power.%20The%20requirements%20for%20documentation%20themselves%20discriminate%20against%20Muslim%2C%20queer%2C%20Dalit%2C%20and%20other%20marginalised%20individuals%20who%20may%20no%20longer%20have%20access%20to%20documents%20in%20Schedule%20IA%20and%20IB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Arvind%20Gunasekar%20further%20criticised%20the%20Empowered%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20lopsided%20composition%2C%20with%20five%20representatives%20from%20the%20central%20government%20and%20only%20one%20from%20the%20state%20government%2C%20as%20a%20blow%20to%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%2C%20with%20its%20requirements%20of%20multiple%20degrees%20of%20verification%2C%20attestation%2C%20and%20authentication%2C%20exclude%20those%20without%20the%20capacity%20or%20resources%20to%20collate%20an%20application%20with%20such%20a%20degree%20of%20detail%20and%20depth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpibhomeaffairs%2Fstatus%2F1767173421727711374%3Fs%3D48%26t%3D--AhA7WzCMM-FRLlO2DKmg%5C%22%3Ehome%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20that%20the%20application%20process%20would%20be%20conducted%20via%20a%20digital%20portal.%20The%20assumption%20of%20access%20to%20digital%20sources%20is%20a%20flawed%20notion%20that%20is%20unmindful%20of%20the%20difficulties%20of%20such%20a%20process%2C%20as%20well%20as%20privacy%20and%20security%20concerns%20in%20the%20handling%20of%20sensitive%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20a%20space%20where%20the%20act%20of%20protesting%20has%20increasingly%20been%20connected%20with%20prosecution%2C%20persecution%2C%20and%20a%20violent%20imposition%20of%20visibility%20on%20activists%20and%20minority%20communities%2C%20what%20responsibility%20do%20Indians%20have%20toward%20resisting%20the%20CAA%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20physical%20evidence%20of%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsafecity.in%2Fwall-painting-at-shaheen-bagh-with-fearless-collective%2F%5C%22%3EFearless%20Collective%E2%80%99s%20mural%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20cleared%20away%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20there%20still%20remains%20an%20air%20of%20resilience.%20Such%20a%20resilience%20is%20a%20peaceful%20one%20grounded%20in%20faith%20in%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECases%20contending%20with%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20however%2C%20remain%20pending%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20has%20limited%20faith%20in%20the%20courts%20and%20finds%20protests%20challenging%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20situation%20currently%20faced%20by%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambu%20Border%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20powerlessness%20can%20pervade%20those%20who%20are%20concerned.%20This%20feeling%20of%20being%20stuck%20complicates%20our%20moral%20compass.%20How%20do%20we%20respond%20when%20those%20we%20are%20resisting%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20political%20party%20or%20regime%2C%20but%20rather%20our%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20neighbours%2C%20coworkers%2C%20and%20loved%20ones%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20restores%20our%20resilience%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20government.%20It%20reaffirms%20faith%20in%20the%20potential%20for%20peaceful%20protests.%20However%2C%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Rules%20raises%20concerns%20for%20Muslim-majority%20community%20spaces%20across%20the%20country%2C%20where%20right-wing%20groups%20may%20intensify%20their%20activities%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20violence.%20A%20morally%20upright%20government%20and%20executive%20would%20ethically%20improve%20security%20measures%20to%20prevent%20such%20risks%20of%20violence%2C%20without%20infringing%20upon%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20constitutional%20right%20to%20protest.%20It%20would%20also%20address%20hate%20towards%20minorities%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20questions%20remain%3A%20How%20far%20will%20states%20resist%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20imposition%20of%20the%20CAA%3F%20How%20much%20can%20they%20resist%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Centre%20has%20repeatedly%20stated%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20not%20intended%20for%20citizens%2C%20differs%20from%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens%2C%20and%20is%20solely%20intended%20for%20foreigners%2C%20the%20guidelines%20for%20accessing%20a%20digital%20certificate%20of%20registration%20seem%20relevant%20in%20their%20applicability%20to%20any%20suspected%20%E2%80%98foreigners%E2%80%99%20in%20India%2C%20along%20with%20their%20connections%20to%20the%20NPR%20and%20NRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20will%20those%20with%20relative%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20cultural%20capital%20choose%20not%20to%20register%20themselves%20under%20the%20discriminatory%20Act%20as%20an%20act%20of%20protest%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opindia.com%2F2019%2F12%2Fharsh-mander-register-muslim-citizenship-amendment-bill%2F%5C%22%3EAs%20Harsh%20Mander%20once%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20one%20register%20as%20Muslim%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Muslim%20siblings%2C%20choose%20to%20suffer%20the%20exclusions%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20not%20show%20documents%2C%20and%20invite%20punishment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20far%20should%20Indian%20citizens%20go%20and%20what%20constitutional%20measures%20are%20tenable%20in%20the%20long-term%20resistance%20of%20an%20unconstitutional%20Act%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20draw%20near%2C%20these%20questions%20are%20likely%20to%20find%20greater%20clarity.%20Those%20who%20care%20are%20likely%20to%20feel%20more%20anxious%2C%20powerless%2C%20and%20stuck%2C%20despite%20the%20courage%2C%20community%2C%20and%20solidarity%20found%20in%20peaceful%20resistance.%20But%20beyond%20our%20calls%20to%20remember%2C%20beyond%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHum%20Dekhenge%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20beyond%20just%20memory%2C%20this%20is%20now%20a%20moment%20to%20contend%20with%20what%20courage%20means%20to%20each%20of%20us%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20we%20would%20put%20ourselves%20in%20harm%E2%80%99s%20way%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%20to%20help%20those%20harmed%20by%20majoritarian%20exclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.%20Manivannan%20is%20a%20scholar%20of%20care%20and%20grief%20in%20protests%20at%20the%20University%20of%20St%20Andrews%20and%20tweets%20%40q_ueering%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710239440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12182004%2FTanushree-Bhasin-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funderstanding-caa-rules-the-process-and-what-it-means-to-resist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20notification%20of%20Rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20is%20a%20predictable%20turn%20in%20electoral%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funderstanding-caa-rules-the-process-and-what-it-means-to-resist%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italian%20Michelin-starred%20chef%20convicted%20after%2053%20people%20fell%20ill%20from%20contaminated%20clams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710238680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-mergozzo-lkw-lake-italy_6487843.jpg%3F20240312104547%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fitalian-michelin-starred-chef-convicted-afte