would%20make%20me%20happy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Pinky%2C%20too%2C%20was%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20do%20something%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20highlighted%20above%2C%20she%20found%20her%20answer%20at%20the%20temple%20that%20changed%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20tonnes%20of%20flowers%20were%20being%20dumped%20into%20the%20river%20daily.%20I%20found%20a%20company%20that%20was%20recycling%20flowers%20and%20asked%20for%20their%20help.%20They%20asked%20for%20my%20profile%20and%20said%20that%20they%20would%20let%20me%20know%20if%20they%20deemed%20it%20fit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20reply%20fuelled%20Poonam%E2%80%99s%20desire%20further%20and%20cemented%20her%20desire%20to%20look%20for%20solutions%20of%20her%20own.%20She%20was%20no%20longer%20going%20to%20let%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20opinions%20define%20her%20self-worth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20looked%20for%20what%20she%20could%20make%20with%20recycled%20floral%20waste%2C%20she%20came%20across%20a%20small%20business%20near%20her%20house%20who%20used%20cow%20dung%20powder%20to%20make%20incense%20sticks.%20Could%20she%20do%C2%A0the%20same%20with%20flowers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20space%20provided%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Poonam%20set%20up%20her%20unit.%20From%20June%202019%2C%20she%20will%20get%20up%20at%205%20am%20and%20go%20to%20temples%20near%20her%20residence.%20There%2C%20she%20would%20request%20the%20staff%20to%20give%20her%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20obliged%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20mixed%20with%20other%20waste.%3C%2Fp